bacon%20bits.%20There%20were%20bacon%20bits%20on%20my%20wedge%20salad.%20As%20a%20semi-observant%20Jewish%20guest%20sitting%20down%20to%20a%20private%20dinner%20at%20the%20swank%20Capitol%20Hill%20Club%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20I%20debated%20whether%20to%20speak%20up.%20Then%20Cheyne%20Day%2C%20who%20teaches%20the%20Christian%20Bible%20to%20lawmakers%20in%20Arkansas%2C%20did%20it%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20have%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Day%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMe%20neither%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20waiter%20brought%20us%20new%20bacon-free%20salads.%20I%20soon%20learned%20that%20Day%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20a%20devout%20Christian%2C%20was%20a%20more%20observant%20follower%20of%20the%20Torah%20than%20I%20was.%20He%20had%20a%20mezuzah%20on%20his%20door%2C%20celebrated%20Hanukkah%2C%20read%20the%20weekly%20Torah%20portion%20in%20Hebrew%20plus%20some%20Talmud%2C%20and%20occasionally%20worshiped%20in%20synagogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Lord%20placed%20that%20on%20my%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20love%20for%20Israel.%26quot%3B%20He%20had%20been%20to%20Israel%20twice%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0once%20shortly%20after%20the%202014%20Gaza%20war.%20He'd%20lobbied%20Arkansas%20lawmakers%20to%20fund%20Israeli%20defense%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Iron%20Dome.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20separate%20the%20land%20from%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20side%20of%20our%20table%20was%20listening%20closely.%20One%20attendee%20offered%20the%20opinion%20that%20it%20wasn't%20exclusively%20Jews%20who%20were%20exiled%20from%20Egypt%20in%20Exodus.%20It%20was%20%3Cem%3Emostly%3C%2Fem%3E%20Jews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJews%20who%20reject%20Christ%20today%20are%20not%20God's%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%2C%20in%20the%20flat%2C%20decisive%20tone%20of%20a%20preacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMmm%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20said%20Day.%20%26quot%3BBe%20careful%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20person%20doubled%20down%3A%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20without%20Christ%20is%20lost!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDay%20took%20a%20breath.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20very%20careful%20to%20say%20it%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20two%20Bible%20teachers%20weren't%20there%20to%20argue%20about%20how%20far%20Jews%20had%20fallen%20from%20God's%20grace.%20This%20was%20a%20gathering%20of%20the%20armies%20of%20Christ%20in%20exile.%20They%20were%20there%20to%20turn%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%94%20democratically%2C%20fairly%2C%20legally%20%E2%80%94%20into%20a%20Christian%20nation%2C%20along%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20in%20the%20most%20direct%20way%20possible%2C%20by%20burrowing%20into%20the%20souls%20of%20lawmakers.%20Our%20host%2C%20Capitol%20Ministries%2C%20gathers%20politicians%20around%20the%20globe%20into%20specially%20tailored%2C%20exclusive%20Bible%20studies.%20The%20dinner%20at%20the%20Capitol%20Hill%20Club%2C%20part%20of%20Capitol%20Ministries'%20global%20summit%2C%20was%20organized%20to%20honor%20Rick%20Perry%2C%20the%20former%20energy%20secretary%20who%20is%20a%20leading%20light%20of%20a%20weekly%20Capitol%20Ministries%20Bible%20study%20for%20Trump%20Cabinet%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Silver%20engraved%20plate%20for%20Governor%20Rick%20Perry%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd049ece7f1785b2e40933%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECapitol%20Ministries%20honored%20Rick%20Perry%2C%20the%20former%20Texas%20governor%20and%20Trump-era%20Cabinet%20member%2C%20with%20an%20award.%3Cp%3ECheriss%20May%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20occurring%20as%20it%20did%20as%20Trump%20was%20formally%20consolidating%20his%20front-runner%20status%20for%20the%20GOP%20nomination%2C%20the%20event%20had%20an%20anticipatory%20feel%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20gathering%20momentum.%20Several%20Republican%20members%20of%20Congress%20were%20present%2C%20and%20after%20dinner%20the%20group%20would%20march%20over%20to%20the%20Capitol%20to%20sanctify%20the%20building%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20its%20current%20leader%2C%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%20%E2%80%94%20a%20stalwart%20Christian%20soldier%20if%20ever%20there%20was%20one.%20But%20as%20Trump%20plotted%20his%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20avoid%20thinking%20about%20the%20biggest%20prize%20of%20all%3A%20next%20year%20in%20the%20West%20Wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20the%20bickering%20Bible%20teachers%20represented%20the%20two%20sides%20of%20our%20host%20and%20Capitol%20Ministries'%20founder%2C%20Ralph%20Drollinger.%20The%20fire-and-brimstone%20ideologue%20across%20the%20table%20embodied%20Drollinger's%20teachings%20%E2%80%94%20a%20doctrinaire%20literalist%20view%2C%20where%20every%20word%20of%20the%20Christian%20Bible%20is%20the%20ironclad%20word%20of%20God.%20Day%20was%20displaying%20the%20more%20diplomatic%2C%20ecumenical%20style%20that%20has%20helped%20Drollinger%20plant%20himself%20into%20so%20many%20centers%20of%20global%20power%2C%20especially%20Washington.%20And%20somewhere%20between%20those%20two%20poles%20was%20the%20secret%20that%20had%20kept%20the%20GOP%20on%20its%20feet%20over%20the%20past%20eight%20years%2C%20with%20Trump%20carrying%20the%20party's%20banner%20and%20millions%20of%20evangelicals%20setting%20aside%20their%20qualms%20and%20falling%20in%20line%20behind%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20rise%20of%20Capitol%20Ministries%20was%20engineered%20by%20its%207-foot-tall%20founder%2C%20Drollinger%2C%20a%20former%20NBA%20center.%20He%20was%20sitting%20a%20few%20feet%20away%20at%20the%20head%20table%2C%20with%20Alex%20Acosta%20and%20Perry%2C%20two%20of%20his%20Bible%20students%20who%20had%20served%20in%20Trump's%20Cabinet%20(Acosta%20was%20secretary%20of%20labor%2C%20Perry%20ran%20the%20Department%20of%20Energy).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dinner%20was%20being%20held%20in%20honor%20of%20Perry%2C%20who%20had%20flown%20in%20from%20Texas%20for%20the%20occasion.%20After%20the%20main%20course%20was%20served%2C%20Drollinger%20stood%20up%20to%20roast%20Perry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20do%20look%20good%20tonight%2C%20compared%20to%20Friday%20mornings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Perry%20looked%20good.%20The%20former%20Texas%20governor%20had%20the%20craggy%20face%20of%20a%20Hollywood%20gunslinger.%20At%2073%2C%20he%20looked%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eready%20to%20lead%20a%20wagon%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20did%20show%20up%20without%20his%20shirt%20on%20one%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20Drollinger%20went%20on.%20%26quot%3BFortunately%2C%20some%20of%20the%20female%20members%20of%20our%20study%20had%20not%20yet%20arrived.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20to%20which%20Perry%20had%20arrived%20shirtless%20was%20a%20Drollinger-led%20gathering%20of%20the%20Trump%20Cabinet%20Bible%20study.%20The%20study%2C%20which%20Drollinger%20launched%20during%20Trump's%20presidency%2C%20has%20hosted%20a%20rotating%20group%20of%20Trump%20appointees%20including%20Mike%20Pompeo%2C%20Betsy%20DeVos%2C%20Sonny%20Perdue%2C%20Ben%20Carson%2C%20and%20Jeff%20Sessions.%20After%20Trump%20left%20the%20White%20House%2C%20the%20study%20went%20remote.%20It%20continues%20to%20meet%20weekly%2C%20over%20Zoom%2C%20every%20Friday%20morning.%20Drollinger%20has%20logged%20in%20from%20Seoul%2C%20Kathmandu%2C%20and%20Bogot%C3%A1.%20Trump's%20departure%20from%20the%20White%20House%20hasn't%20stopped%20him%20from%20using%20the%20old%20administration's%20star%20power%20to%20fuel%20Capitol%20Ministries'%20growth.%20It%20now%20teaches%20old-school%20Christianity%20to%20politicians%20in%2060%20world%20capitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Iowa%20caucuses%20only%20a%20few%20weeks%20away%2C%20the%20prospect%20that%20Drollinger's%20Zoom%20group%20of%20White%20House%20exiles%20might%20return%20to%20power%20was%20suddenly%20very%20real.%20But%20regardless%20of%20what%20happens%20this%20coming%20November%2C%20Capitol%20Ministries%20is%20quickly%20becoming%20the%20face%20of%20American%20GOP-style%20evangelicalism%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dozens%20of%20Drollinger-trained%20teachers%20at%20the%20Capitol%20Hill%20Club%20had%20come%20from%20as%20far%20away%20as%20Rwanda%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20the%20South%20Pacific.%20Other%20than%20Ralph's%20wife%2C%20Danielle%2C%20and%20a%20few%20members%20of%20Capitol%20Ministries'%20administrative%20staff%2C%20the%20room%20was%20almost%20entirely%20men.%20When%20Drollinger%20lit%20into%20Perry%20with%20his%20lighthearted%20locker-room%20ribbing%2C%20they%20put%20down%20their%20forks%20and%20chuckled.%20Here%20was%20an%20anecdote%20of%20fellowship%20and%20intimacy%20that%20seemed%20to%20underscore%20their%20own%20proximity%20to%20power.%20They%20were%2C%20after%20all%2C%20part%20of%20an%20exclusive%20group%20that%20got%20to%20see%20Rick%20Perry%20as%20he%20really%20was%20%E2%80%94%20unburdening%20his%20soul%2C%20using%20the%20Bible%20to%20unpack%20the%20riddles%20of%20leadership.%20Sometimes%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20without%20a%20shirt.%20Their%20laughter%20seemed%20to%20encourage%20Drollinger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rick%20Perry%20speaking%20to%20Ralph%20Drollinger%20on%20stage%20at%20Capitol%20Ministries.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd04cdce7f1785b2e4094d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERick%20Perry%20spoke%20to%20Drollinger%20at%20Capitol%20Ministries'%20global%20summit%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3Cp%3ECheriss%20May%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDrollinger%20shifted%2C%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20to%20a%20more%20pastoral%20mode.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20blessing%20you've%20been%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Casting%20his%20eye%20forward%20to%20November%202024%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BHopefully%20certain%20things%20will%20happen%20next%20year%20around%20this%20time.%20We'll%20have%20our%20cabinet%20study%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECertain%20things%20will%20happen.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Drollinger%20was%2C%20to%20my%20ears%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20reelection%20of%20Donald%20Trump.%20While%20Capitol%20Ministries%20doesn't%20formally%20endorse%20political%20candidates%2C%20Drollinger%20wasn't%20shy%20about%20sharing%20his%20personal%20enthusiasm%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20second%20Trump%20presidency.%20I%20had%20already%20heard%20a%20series%20of%20justifications%2C%20some%20from%20Ralph%20directly%20and%20some%20from%20his%20Bible%20studies%20when%20I%20profiled%20him%20for%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F10%2F29%2Fmagazine%2Fralph-drollinger-white-house-evangelical.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202019%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20like%20Samson%20%E2%80%94%20rough%20and%20tough%2C%20with%20interesting%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20like%20the%20ox%20in%20Proverbs%2014%3A4%20%E2%80%94%20lots%20of%20crops%20harvested%2C%20lots%20of%20shit%20to%20clean%20out%20of%20the%20stable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20the%20one%20who%20had%20been%20chosen%20by%20the%20voters%2C%20so%20his%20constitutional%20authority%20deserved%20everyone's%20respect%2C%20as%20per%20Matthew%2022%3A21%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Brender%20unto%20Caesar%20the%20things%20that%20are%20Caesar's.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20last%20point%20rang%20hollow%20to%20me%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Trump's%20ongoing%20refusal%20to%20accept%20his%202020%20loss.%20I%20had%20shown%20up%20to%20the%20Capitol%20Hill%20Club%20partly%20to%20hear%20which%20biblical%20circumlocutions%20Drollinger%20would%20use%20to%20justify%20his%20continued%20affinity%20for%20Trump%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20attack%2C%20though%20I%20already%20knew%2C%20deep%20down%2C%20that%20certain%20traits%20he%20shared%20with%20his%20congressional%20clientele%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pragmatic%20flexibility%2C%20combined%20with%20an%20attraction%20to%20power%20%E2%80%94%20didn't%20leave%20him%20with%20much%20of%20a%20choice.%20There%20was%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20a%20lot%20more%20shit%20in%20the%20stable.%20But%20the%20farmers%20were%20still%20standing%20by%20their%20ox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20was%20more%20interested%20in%20Perry%2C%20who%20had%20called%20Trump%20%26quot%3Ba%20cancer%20on%20conservatism%26quot%3B%20before%20joining%20his%20Cabinet.%20Then%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20scandal%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20phone%20call%26quot%3B%20with%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20which%20Perry%20had%20helped%20arrange%2C%20he%20resigned.%20He'd%20campaigned%20for%20Trump%20in%202020%2C%20but%20now%2C%20with%20the%202024%20cycle%20taking%20shape%20and%20the%20Iowa%20caucuses%20weeks%20away%2C%20he%20had%20still%20not%20endorsed%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20lapse%20did%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20lost%20on%20Drollinger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20guys%20in%20the%20Trump%20Cabinet%20feel%20like%20they're%20in%20exile%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20think%20that%20way%2C%20Rick%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerry%20didn't%20say%20a%20word.%20He%20just%20sat%20there%2C%20scrolling%20through%20his%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20paying%20attention%20right%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerry%20looked%20up.%20He%20gave%20Drollinger%20a%20quick%20nod.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20had%20witnessed%20a%20bit%20of%20daylight%20between%20the%20two%20friends%20on%20the%20Trump%20question.%20I%20was%20wrong.%20Talking%20to%20Perry%20later%2C%20I%20learned%20he%20was%20no%20less%20enthusiastic%20than%20Drollinger%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20a%20Trump%20victory%20and%20the%20return%20of%20a%20Drollinger-led%20Trump%20Cabinet%20Bible%20study.%20It%20was%20true%20that%20Perry%20had%20not%20endorsed%20Trump%20yet%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BI'm%20keeping%20my%20powder%20dry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20my%20endorsement%20matters.%26quot%3B%20But%20the%20glimmer%20of%20dissent%20that%20I%20thought%20I%20had%20witnessed%20at%20the%20Capitol%20Hill%20Club%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20projection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20person%20Perry%20was%20ready%20to%20stump%20for%20was%20Ralph%20Drollinger.%20%26quot%3BI%20wish%20I%20could%20have%20grown%20up%20with%20access%20to%20Ralph%20Drollinger's%20Bible%20studies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAllow%20for%20the%20Bible%20to%20be%20your%20checklist%2C%20whether%20you're%20running%20your%20personal%20life%2C%20your%20family%2C%20your%20state%2C%20or%20your%20country.%20Use%20the%20Bible%20as%20your%20checklist%2C%20and%20your%20success%20will%20be%20enhanced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rick%20Perry%20speaking%20into%20a%20microphone%20with%20his%20finger%20pointed%20out.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd051e90413ab8e1d6f918%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERick%20Perry%20spoke%20at%20the%20Capitol%20Minsteries%20global%20summit.%3Cp%3ECheriss%20May%20for%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn't%20my%20first%20experience%20watching%20Drollinger%20minister%20to%20political%20principals.%20In%202019%2C%20I%20flew%20with%20Drollinger%20to%20Nicaragua%2C%20to%20sit%20in%20with%20him%20during%20a%20lengthy%20meeting%20with%20Daniel%20Ortega%2C%20the%20country's%20strongman%20president.%20As%20he%20often%20does%2C%20Drollinger%20brought%20along%20his%20wife%2C%20Danielle%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20a%20California%20political%20action%20committee.%20The%20idea%20to%20found%20Capitol%20Ministries%20was%20born%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20on%20their%20second%20date%2C%20and%20while%20Ralph%20is%20the%20public%20face%20of%20the%20organization%2C%20Danielle%20is%20arguably%20his%20most%20influential%20advisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrollinger%20was%20looking%20to%20plant%20a%20Bible%20study%20in%20the%20Nicaraguan%20capital.%20He%20wanted%20me%20there%20to%20attest%20that%20he%20wasn't%20cutting%20backroom%20deals%20to%20engineer%20a%20worldwide%20takeover%20by%20Christian%20evangelicals.%20And%20indeed%2C%20he%20wasn't.%20Instead%2C%20he%20was%20simply%20teaching%20his%20version%20of%20the%20Bible%20to%20political%20leaders%20and%20letting%20them%20do%20the%20rest.%20The%20result%20was%20a%20mix%20of%20American%20family-values%20conservativism%20and%20contemporary%20Trumpism%3A%20According%20to%20Capitol%20Ministries'%20interpretation%20of%20biblical%20doctrine%2C%20marriage%20is%20an%20institution%20where%20men%20should%20take%20the%20lead%2C%20homosexuality%20is%20ungodly%2C%20abortion%20is%20infanticide%2C%20climate%20change%20is%20unproven%20at%20best%2C%20and%20family%20separation%20at%20the%20Southern%20border%20is%20a%20reasonable%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20might%20society%20look%20like%20if%20redrawn%20along%20such%20lines%3F%20That%20was%2C%20after%20all%2C%20Drollinger's%20hope.%20He%20wanted%20his%20version%20of%20the%20Bible%20to%20be%20adopted%20by%20political%20leaders%2C%20ratified%20by%20voters%20through%20the%20democratic%20process%2C%20and%20then%20institutionalized.%20That%20wouldn't%20be%20a%20patriarchal%20theocracy%2C%20not%20exactly.%20It%20would%20just%20be%20the%20same%20set%20of%20policies%20that%20a%20theocracy%20would%20most%20likely%20want%2C%20achieved%20through%20democratic%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Christian-ends-through-democratic-means%20stance%20was%20easier%20to%20defend%20in%202019.%20That%20was%20before%20Trump%20made%20clear%20his%20willingness%20to%20torch%20the%20most%20basic%20democratic%20norms%20for%20a%20chance%20at%20another%20four%20years%20in%20power.%20Even%20if%20I%20didn't%20agree%20with%20everything%20Drollinger%20had%20to%20say%20back%20then%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20a%20fairly%20reasonable%20journalistic%20decision%20to%20give%20his%20views%20a%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20things%20were%20more%20complicated.%20The%20thing%20is%2C%20I%20%3Cem%3Eliked%20%3C%2Fem%3EDrollinger.%20Even%20after%20we%20left%20Washington%2C%20I%20kept%20on%20sending%20him%20holiday%20cards.%20I%20had%20been%20rather%20hard%20on%20him%20in%20print%2C%20and%20he'd%20been%20a%20good%20sport%20about%20it.%20We%20both%20felt%20like%20outsiders%20in%20Washington%20%E2%80%94%20too%20candid%2C%20too%20trusting%20%E2%80%94%20but%20our%20relationship%20was%20Washingtonian%20to%20the%20core%2C%20a%20bilateral%20seduction.%20I%20had%20witnessed%20firsthand%20Drollinger's%20ability%20to%20effortlessly%20arrange%20weird%20triangles%20of%20self-interest%20like%20the%20one%20with%20Ortega%2C%20these%20webs%20of%20relationships%20that%20are%20underwritten%20by%20a%20transactional%20logic%20and%20yet%20somehow%20don't%20feel%20transactional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20year%2C%20Drollinger%20told%20me%20about%20another%20story%20that%20he%20wanted%20told.%20This%20was%20the%20story%20of%20Capitol%20Ministries%20eclipsing%20a%20longtime%20competitor%2C%20the%20Fellowship.%20Like%20Capitol%20Ministries%2C%20the%20Fellowship%20serves%20evangelical%20politicians%20looking%20to%20practice%20their%20faith%20in%20a%20group%20setting%2C%20while%20holding%20itself%20out%20worldwide%20as%20a%20portal%20to%20what%20might%20be%20called%20Beltway%20Christianity.%20It%20was%20also%2C%20until%20recently%2C%20the%20organizer%20of%20the%20National%20Prayer%20Breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20point%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20give%20Drollinger%20his%20due.%20Capitol%20Ministries%20was%20eating%20the%20Fellowship's%20lunch.%20Douglas%20Coe%2C%20the%20well-connected%20evangelical%20who%20engineered%20the%20Fellowship's%20rise%2C%20died%20in%202017%20(the%20Fellowship%20didn't%20respond%20to%20my%20requests%20for%20comment).%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20vaunted%20National%20Prayer%20Breakfast%20had%20become%20overrun%20by%20unregistered%20foreign%20agents%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Maria%20Butina%2C%20a%20bona%20fide%20Russian%20spy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Congress%20essentially%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etook%20it%20over%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20hybrid%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fnational-prayer-breakfast-congress-takeover-private-religious-group%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20remote%20event%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20the%20senators%2C%20members%20of%20Congress%2C%20and%20a%20select%20group%20of%20their%20vetted%20guests%20would%20be%20kept%20a%20safe%20distance%20away%20from%20the%20international%20men%20of%20mystery%20and%20assorted%20Beltway%20hustlers%20who%20once%20paid%20handsomely%20to%20rub%20their%20shoulders%20at%20the%20Washington%20Hilton.%20The%20breakfast%20is%20still%20a%20big%20event.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20showed%20up%20for%20it%20this%20year%2C%20at%20National%20Statuary%20Hall%20inside%20the%20Capitol.%20But%20now%20that%20the%20breakfast%20is%20being%20run%20by%20a%20new%20foundation%2C%20the%20Fellowship%20has%20been%20pushed%20to%20the%20sidelines.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Capitol%20Ministries%2C%20clean%20as%20a%20whistle%2C%20had%20set%20up%20shop%20on%20every%20inhabited%20continent%2C%2043%20US%20state%20capitals%2C%20plus%20the%20three%20weekly%20studies%20that%20Drollinger%20himself%20hosted%20%E2%80%94%20one%20for%20the%20Senate%2C%20one%20for%20the%20House%2C%20and%20one%20for%20the%20Trump%20Cabinet%20alumni.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20what%20Capitol%20Ministries%20offers%20members%20is%20meat-and-potatoes%20spiritual%20guidance%2C%20what%20Drollinger%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh-protein%20diet.%26quot%3B%20Democracy%20pulls%20elected%20officials%20away%20from%20their%20families%20and%20thrusts%20them%20into%20an%20unfamiliar%20environment%20with%20a%20number%20of%20trapdoors.%20Capitol%20Ministries%20offers%20them%20a%20safe%20spiritual%20anchorage.%20They%20are%20gently%20counseled%20to%20stay%20loyal%20to%20their%20spouses%2C%20attentive%20to%20their%20children%2C%20humble%20before%20their%20constituents%2C%20and%20to%20refrain%20from%20alcohol.%20The%20%26quot%3BMinistry%20Leadership%20Training%2C%26quot%3B%20a%2031-page%20workbook%2C%20offers%20more%20clues%20to%20the%20organization's%20success.%20It%20identifies%20%26quot%3Bproblem%20group%26quot%3B%20competitors%20%E2%80%94%20the%20religious%20right%2C%20the%20Fellowship%2C%20WallBuilders%2C%20and%20official%20state-salaried%20chaplains%20%E2%80%94%20and%20counsels%20the%20kind%20of%20calm%2C%20divinely%20informed%20forbearance%20that%20Drollinger%20himself%20embodies.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20recognize%20that%20we%20are%20not%20in%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20workbook%20says%2C%20quoting%20Ben%20Carson.%20%26quot%3BGod%20is%20in%20control.%26quot%3B%20It%20later%20adds%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20experience%20here%2C%20the%20attacks%20and%20the%20battles%2C%20they're%20nothing%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20eternity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%20at%20the%20Capitol%20Hill%20Club%2C%20we%20poured%20out%20onto%20the%20sidewalk.%20Perry%20jumped%20into%20a%20black%20SUV.%20The%20Drollingers%20headed%20back%20to%20their%20hotel.%20The%20rest%20of%20us%20walked%20over%20to%20the%20Rotunda.%20Two%20Republican%20members%20of%20Congress%2C%20both%20Bible-study%20attendees%2C%20would%20be%20giving%20us%20a%20private%20nighttime%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bruce%20Westerman%20speaking%20to%20night-time%20tour%20group%20in%20the%20Capitol.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd074ace7f1785b2e40a73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20Bruce%20Westerman%20led%20a%20night-time%20tour%20group.%3Cp%3ECheriss%20May%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20members%20was%20Rep.%20Bruce%20Westerman%20of%20Arkansas%2C%20whose%20manner%20reminded%20me%20of%20Drollinger%20%E2%80%94%20conciliatory%2C%20polished%2C%20low-key.%20The%20other%20was%20Rep.%20Glenn%20%26quot%3BGT%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20a%20history%20buff%20with%20a%20solid%20build%20and%20straight-shooting%2C%20blue-collar%20presentation.%20Thompson%20had%20made%20a%20career%20in%20nursing%20homes%2C%20starting%20off%20as%20an%20orderly%20working%20the%20overnight%20shift%20before%20being%20promoted%20to%20administrator.%20The%20two%20men%20led%20a%20group%20of%20about%2030%20Bible-study%20teachers%20through%20the%20metal%20detectors%2C%20past%20the%20%26quot%3BMembers%20Only%26quot%3B%20signs%2C%20and%20into%20the%20very%20center%20of%20the%20Rotunda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20looked%20up%20at%20the%20ceiling%20and%20sang%20%26quot%3BTo%20God%20Be%20the%20Glory.%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20claimed%20that%20the%20paintings%20around%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Rotunda%20all%20have%20a%20biblical%20theme%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%20interesting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20the%20separation%20of%20church%20and%20state.%26quot%3B%20He%20pointed%20out%20the%20central%20figure%2C%20George%20Washington%20rising%20up%20into%20the%20heavens%2C%20accompanied%20by%20the%20goddesses%20of%20Fame%20and%20Liberty%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enot%20biblical%20exactly%2C%20but%20certainly%20beyond%20the%20realm%20of%20mortal%20experience.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20really%20because%20of%20Washington's%20humility%20that%20we%20do%20not%20have%20a%20monarchy%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20followed%20Thompson%20and%20Westerman%20out%20onto%20a%20balcony%20overlooking%20the%20Mall.%20I%20tried%20to%20make%20some%20small%20talk%20with%20Thompson%20about%20his%20district%2C%20but%20it%20turned%20out%20that%20Worlds%20End%20State%20Park%2C%20a%20three-hour%20drive%20northwest%20of%20Philadelphia%2C%20was%20still%20to%20the%20east%20of%20his%20district.%20Thompson%20was%20gracious%20about%20it.%20But%20I%20still%20felt%20the%20inverse%20form%20of%20the%20awkwardness%20that%20I%20had%20experienced%20during%20the%20bacon-bits%20dinner-table%20exchange.%20I%20had%20assumed%20that%20GT%20Thompson%20and%20I%20shared%20a%20common%20identity%20as%20Pennsylvanians%2C%20and%20that%20it%20meant%20I%20knew%20something%20about%20the%20land%20where%20Thompson%20was%20from.%20I%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20inside%2C%20a%20small%20crowd%20had%20gathered%20around%20a%20short%2C%20youthful%20man%20with%20the%20aggressive%20earnestness%20of%20a%20high-school%20debate%20coach%20or%20game-show%20host.%20It%20was%20Mike%20Johnson%2C%20the%20speaker%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20a%20spiritual%20battle%20for%20the%20future%20of%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20future%20of%20freedom%20around%20the%20world.%20What's%20happening%20in%20Israel%20right%20now%20has%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20people's%20attention.%20And%20I%20think%20what%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20is%20exactly%20right.%20This%20is%20a%20battle%20of%20good%20versus%20evil.%20Light%20versus%20darkness.%20Civilization%20versus%20barbarism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20took%20different%20forms%20in%20different%20places%2C%20he%20said.%20In%20the%20US%20theater%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20need%20all%20the%20prayer%20we%20can%20get.%20And%20so%20these%20ministries%20in%20the%20Capitol%2C%20this%20is%20pivotal%20stuff.%20This%20is%20important%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20leaders%20laid%20hands%20on%20Johnson.%20They%20closed%20their%20eyes.%20They%20prayed%20over%20him.%20A%20member%20of%20Johnson's%20staff%20then%20ushered%20us%20into%20the%20Congressional%20Prayer%20Room%2C%20a%20tall%2C%20narrow%20alcove%20dominated%20by%20a%20stained-glass%20portrait%20of%20Washington%2C%20kneeling%20in%20prayer%2C%20and%20four%20words%20from%20the%20Gettysburg%20Address%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20Nation%20Under%20God.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Johnson%20putting%20his%20head%20down%20with%20ministry%20leaders'%20hands%20on%20his%20shoulder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd059690413ab8e1d6f94f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECapitol%20Ministry%20leaders%20prayed%20over%20House%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson.%3Cp%3ECheriss%20May%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20the%20members%20took%20us%20onto%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives.%20Thompson%20scrupulously%20pointed%20out%20the%20room's%20religious%20iconography%20including%20a%20bust%20of%20Moses%20along%20its%20centerline%2C%20high%20up%20on%20a%20wall.%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20founders%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2012%2F08%2F02%2F157777697%2Fcue-the-tape-how-david-barton-sees-the-world%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2522%255BOf%2520the%255D%252056%2520who%2Cmean%2520a%2520Bible%2520school%2520degree.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseminary%20degrees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said%2C%20a%20claim%20that%20has%20been%20fact-checked%20and%20debunked%20by%20NPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20the%20media%20black%20out%20'In%20God%20We%20Trust'%3F%26quot%3B%20someone%20asked%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20words%20carved%20into%20the%20black%20marble%20above%20the%20speaker's%20rostrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20may%20be%20tempted%2C%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCensorship!%26quot%3B%20someone%20muttered%20under%20their%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20noticed%20that%20TV%20cameras%20will%20often%20leave%20those%20words%20out%20of%20the%20frame%2C%26quot%3B%20Westerman%20offered.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20that's%20intentional%20or%20what.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20voice%20piped%20up%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20your%20most%20memorable%20day%20in%20this%20chamber%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20another%20seat%20in%20the%20chamber%20came%20the%20whisper%3A%20%26quot%3BJanuary%206.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThompson%20took%20the%20cue.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20to%20evacuate%20the%20Capitol%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20stayed%20in%20the%20Capitol%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Westerman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20name%20went%20unmentioned.%20The%20Q%26amp%3BA%20transitioned%20to%20Thompson's%20experiences%20with%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20the%20Israeli%20prime%20minister.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20a%20few%20of%20us%20wondering%20if%20he%20had%20American%20citizenship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20good%20candidate%20for%20president.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20Perry%2C%20I%20thought%20I'd%20glimpsed%20a%20crack%20of%20daylight%20between%20the%20GOP%20leaders%20and%20its%20rank%20and%20file.%20But%20maybe%2C%20as%20with%20Perry%2C%20I%20had%20imagined%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20good%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20said%20of%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWesterman%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BA%20very%20good%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ERalph%20and%20Danielle%20had%20not%20come%20along%20for%20the%20Capitol%20Hill%20tour.%20When%20I%20told%20them%20what%20Johnson%20had%20said%20about%20Israel%2C%20over%20lunch%20a%20few%20of%20days%20later%2C%20the%20Drollingers%20said%20they%20approved%20of%20his%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20wears%20his%20Christianity%20on%20his%20shirtsleeves%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Drollinger%2C%20taking%20a%20pause%20from%20his%20burger.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20why%20God%20elevated%20him.%20I'm%20just%20so%20delighted%20that%20God%20had%20put%20a%20really%20strong%20Christian%20as%20speaker.%20First%20time%20in%20our%20lifetimes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22United%20States%20Congress%20logo%20on%20black%20cowboy%20boots%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dcf3b36080194819fa4723%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlack%20cowboy%20boots%20with%20the%20United%20States%20Congress%20patch.%3Cp%3ECheriss%20May%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Capitol%20Ministries%20international%20conference%20was%20wrapping%20up.%20Bible%20teachers%20from%20all%20around%20the%20world%20were%20milling%20around%20the%20hotel%20lobby%2C%20saying%20goodbyes%20as%20they%20waited%20for%20their%20flights%20home.%20The%20Drollingers%20were%20dressed%20casually.%20For%20a%20guy%20who%20is%207%20feet%20tall%2C%20with%20an%20endless%20stock%20of%20Bible%20quotes%20at%20his%20fingertips%2C%20Drollinger%20has%20a%20striking%20lack%20of%20bombast%2C%20especially%20in%20smaller%20groups.%20He%20speaks%20in%20a%20mellow%20baritone%2C%20presents%20the%20same%20face%20to%20everyone%20he%20meets%2C%20and%20carefully%20considers%20everything%20that's%20said.%20His%20considerate%20approach%20to%20religious%20indoctrination%20recalls%20an%20old%20saying%20about%20negotiation%20%E2%80%94%20be%20firm%2C%20be%20friendly%2C%20be%20fair%3B%20but%20most%20of%20all%2C%20be%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20mainly%20brought%20questions%20about%20Trump.%20The%20Drollingers%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Capitol%20Ministries%20is%20officially%20a%20nonpartisan%20organization%20and%20does%20not%20endorse%20parties%20or%20candidates.%20Whatever%20views%20they%20shared%20with%20me%20about%20Trump%2C%20they%20said%2C%20were%20theirs%20and%20not%20Capitol%20Ministries'.%20Drollinger's%20Washington%20Bible%20studies%2C%20they%20said%2C%20drew%20both%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans%20from%20both%20chambers%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20trying%20to%20cast%20a%20broad%20net%2C%26quot%3B%20Drollinger%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20get%20everybody%20to%20come%20to%20Christ%2C%20from%20every%20political%20party.%20So%20even%20though%20I%20hold%20certain%20political%20views%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20probably%20know%20what%20those%20are%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20lead%20with%20that%20publicly.%20And%20I%20wouldn't%20teach%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20that%20he'd%20like%20to%20see%20the%20return%20of%20a%20cabinet%20Bible%20study%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20Danielle%2C%20perhaps%20worried%20that%20he'd%20veered%20too%20far%20in%20a%20pro-Trump%20direction%2C%20jumped%20in%20to%20clarify%20a%20bit.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20if%20any%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20started%2C%20then%20turned%20to%20her%20husband.%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20agree%20with%20me%20on%20this%3F%20Tell%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20turned%20back%20to%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20Republican%20wins%20the%20primary%20or%20the%20general.%20We%20would%20hope%E2%80%94%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrollinger%20jumped%20in.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20that%20surround%20the%20inner%20atmosphere%20say%20that%20they%20want%20to%20see%20that%20reignited%20no%20matter%20what%20Republican%20gets%20elected.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20we%20end%20up%20with%20a%20Democratic%20president%2C%20I'm%20told%20by%20Scripture%20to%20respect%20the%20office.%20So%20I'm%20going%20to%20try%20to%20build%20a%20relationship%20with%20any%20elected%20leader%20I%20can%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20their%20stripes%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20cause%20of%20Christ.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20whether%20Trump%20had%20respected%20the%20office.%20And%20if%20it%20were%20the%20case%20that%20he%20had%20not%2C%20would%20Scripture%20then%20require%20Christians%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20against%20him%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20jury%20is%20out%20as%20to%20whether%20he's%20an%20insurrectionist%2C%26quot%3B%20Drollinger%20replied.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20the%20tapes%20of%20the%20activities%20would%20indicate%20that.%20I've%20never%20really%20seen%20them.%20But%20I%20would%20be%20on%20the%20side%20of%20grace.%20Even%20if%20Donald%20Trump%20were%20insurrectional%2C%20and%20the%20proof%20on%20that%20were%20patent%2C%20then%20I'd%20still%20be%20willing%20to%20give%20him%20grace%20and%20favor%20a%20relationship%20with%20him.%20Whether%20he's%20the%20president%20or%20not.%20Time%20has%20passed%20and%20we%20all%20grow.%26quot%3B%20Capitol%20Ministries%20had%20board%20members%2C%20he%20said%2C%20who%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20various%20misdeeds%2C%20and%20that%20didn't%20stop%20him%20from%20continuing%20to%20work%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20whether%20there%20would%20be%20anything%20a%20presidential%20candidate%20could%20do%20that%20would%20set%20them%20outside%20the%20mitigating%20power%20of%20grace.%20What%20if%20they%20tried%20to%20rewrite%20the%20Constitution%20to%20end%20elections%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%2C%20now%20we're%20facing%20tyranny%20charges%2C%26quot%3B%20Drollinger%20said%20with%20a%20chuckle.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20against%20the%20law%20and%20punishable%20by%20death%2C%20so%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that.%20I%20would%20stand%20strong%20against%20that.%20That's%20not%20obeying%20the%20governing%20authorities%2C%20which%20is%20Romans%2013.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20between%20that%20hypothetical%20and%20Trump's%20actions%20on%20January%206%2C%20Drollinger%20said%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bhuge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20saw%20as%20political%20pragmatism%2C%20Drollinger%20continued%20to%20frame%20as%20fidelity%20to%20Scripture.%20At%20lunch%2C%20he%20explicitly%20rejected%20pragmatism%20as%20a%20viable%20long-term%20approach%20for%20politicians.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20works%20today%20can%20kill%20you%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you're%20always%20tethered%20to%20Scripture%2C%20you're%20never%20going%20to%20get%20tripped%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ralph%20Drollinger%20seated%20at%20Capitol%20Ministries%20event%20listening%20to%20speaker%20from%20his%20seat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd06e1ce7f1785b2e40a4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERalph%20Drollinger%20sat%20at%20a%20Capitol%20Ministries%20event%20next%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20Danielle.%3Cp%3ECheriss%20May%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brought%20up%20the%20awkward%20conversation%20from%20the%20dinner%20table%2C%20how%20the%20bacon%20bits%20sprinkled%20across%20the%20top%20of%20my%20wedge%20salad%20had%20led%20to%20a%20cascade%20of%20conversation%20about%20Jews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrollinger%2C%20in%20his%20low-key%2C%20agreeable%20way%2C%20cited%20the%20relevant%20passages%20from%20Romans%20and%20Revelation.%20It%20seemed%20he%20did%20not%20entirely%20disagree.%20Anyone%20who%20approached%20these%20texts%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bgrammatical%2C%20historical%2C%20normative%20hermeneutic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20would%20conclude%20%26quot%3Bthat%20when%20the%20Jews%20rejected%20their%20Messiah%2C%20God%20put%20them%20on%20a%20side%20track.%20He%20grafts%20in%20the%20gentiles.%20But%20in%20the%20End%20Times%2C%20he%20brings%20them%20back%20on%20the%20main%20track.%20And%20they're%20leading%20the%20charge%20towards%20the%20second%20coming%20of%20Christ.%20You%20see%20massive%20amounts%20of%20Jews%20%E2%80%94%20144%2C000%20Jews%20%E2%80%94%20become%20the%20greatest%20evangelists%20of%20the%20world%2C%20proclaiming%20the%20second%20coming%20of%20the%20Messiah.%26quot%3B%20Here%2C%20Drollinger%20was%20referring%20to%20Revelation%207%3A4%2C%20which%20gives%2012%2C000%20Jews%20from%20each%20of%20the%2012%20biblical%20tribes%20a%20role%20in%20ushering%20in%20the%20apocalypse%2C%20immediately%20before%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20seventh%20seal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrollinger%20had%20made%20the%20same%20point%20in%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcapmin.org%2Fthe-biblical-basis-for-americas-commitment-to-israel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Bible%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20eight%20days%20after%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%20%26quot%3BGod%20is%20not%20through%20with%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BGod%20has%20a%20huge%20future%20plan%20for%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20whether%20I%20was%20personally%20interfering%20with%20God's%20plan%20by%20not%20converting%20to%20Christianity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Drollinger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20like%20I%20am!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20it'll%20just%20happen%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Drollinger%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20just%20look%20to%20your%20future.%20Make%20sure%20you%20eat%20well%20and%20stay%20alive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20a%20question%20I'd%20often%20wondered%20about%20Trump's%20Cabinet.%20Did%20Drollinger%20believe%20there%20was%20a%20connection%20between%20biblical%20eschatology%20%E2%80%94%20prophecies%20about%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20current%20events%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrollinger%20rubbed%20his%20chin.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20wonder%20if%20Israel%20drops%20the%20second%20shoe%20after%20they%20chase%20Hamas%20out%20of%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20if%20they%20retake%20all%20of%20Gaza%20for%20Israel.%20Because%20there%20are%20passages%20that%20say%2C%20'Until%20Israel%20returns%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Ewhole%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20land%2C%20you%20don't%20start%20the%20eschatological%20clock%20towards%20the%20return%20of%20the%20Messiah.'%26quot%3B%20Incorporating%20Gaza%20into%20Israel%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20return%20to%20Israel%20to%20%26quot%3Bthe%20footprint%20of%20their%20original%20holdings%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20prophetic%20step.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20seem%20constructive%20to%20ask%20whether%20Gaza%20had%20actually%20been%20under%20Israeli%20control%20at%20any%20point%20prior%20to%201967.%20That%20would%20in%20turn%20lead%20to%20even%20thornier%20questions%20about%20archeological%20finds%2C%20the%20historicity%20of%20King%20David%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20Drollinger%20did%20seem%20to%20recognize%20that%20eschatology%20was%20potentially%20dangerous%20ground.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20someone%20driving%20around%20in%20a%20nuclear%20submarine%20reading%20the%20Book%20of%20Revelation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referencing%20the%20film%20%26quot%3BThe%20Hunt%20for%20Red%20October.%26quot%3B%20I%20think%20he%20brought%20this%20up%20because%20of%20his%20instinctive%20courtesy%2C%20his%20desire%20to%20find%20common%20ground.%20He%20wanted%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20point%20I%20was%20making%2C%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20an%20eschatological%20approach%20to%20foreign%20policy%2C%20had%20some%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20on%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20and%20why%20to%20support%20Israel%2C%20Drollinger%20was%20indeed%20looking%20to%20Revelation%20for%20answers.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20but%20he%20was%20teaching%20them%20to%20elected%20officials%20who%20could%20one%20day%20find%20themselves%20issuing%20commands%20to%20nuclear%20submarines.%20And%20this%20wasn't%20just%20in%20our%20off-the-cuff%20lunch%20conversation.%20It%20was%20in%20the%20Capitol%20Ministries%20printed%20Bible%20study%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20which%20cited%20Revelation's%20prophecy%20of%20144%2C000%20Christ-believing%20Jews%20as%20being%20among%20the%20reasons%20that%20US%20leaders%20should%20support%20Israel%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWild%20stuff.%20It's%20even%20wilder%20when%20one%20considers%20that%20within%20the%20radical%20universe%20of%20MAGA-sympathetic%20evangelicalism%2C%20Drollinger%20is%20actually%20something%20of%20a%20moderate.%20Unlike%20David%20Barton%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20WallBuilders%2C%20Drollinger%20doesn't%20endorse%20an%20unconstitutional%20union%20of%20church%20and%20state%2C%20and%20he%20bridles%20when%20leftist%20commentators%20claim%20he's%20a%20Christian%20nationalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20teach%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20lunch%2C%20when%20I%20asked%20him%20about%20biblical%20passages%20that%20prophesy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20get%20a%20big%20crowd%20with%20eschatology%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20really%20meet%20with%20what%20these%20guys%20need.%26quot%3B%20What%20they%20need%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Btaking%20what%20Scripture%20says%20and%20applying%20it%20to%20the%20life%20of%20a%20public%20servant%20specifically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20I%20followed%20up%20by%20email.%20I%20pointed%20out%20the%20apparent%20eschatological%20implications%20of%20Drollinger's%20Bible%20study%20on%20Israel.%20Drollinger%20said%20an%20adjustment%20to%20his%20no-eschatology%20rule%20was%20justified%20by%20the%20turmoil%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20current%20events%20are%20so%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20those%20to%20whom%20I%20minister%20that%20I%20make%20exceptions%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20He%20added%20that%20mentioning%20an%20occasional%20%26quot%3Beschatological%20truth%26quot%3B%20about%20%26quot%3BGod's%20future%20plans%20for%20Israel%26quot%3B%20derived%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20the%20Bible%20itself%26quot%3B%20was%20different%20from%20teaching%20the%20entire%20book%20of%20Revelation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20followed%20up%20with%20two%20clips%20from%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%20Those%20stories%20made%20it%20clear%20he%20wasn't%20alone%20in%20talking%20about%20a%20full%20and%20permanent%20Israeli%20takeover%20of%20Gaza.%20The%20idea%20had%20significant%20traction%20on%20the%20Israeli%20far%20right%20as%20well.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20bind%20Drollinger%20was%20in.%20Should%20he%20just%20ignore%20what%20he%20took%20to%20be%20the%20literal%20word%20of%20God%20when%20it%20seemed%20to%20be%20predicting%20global%20events%20that%20were%20just%20over%20the%20horizon%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20bigger%20issue%20here.%20Once%20you're%20quoting%20the%20Bible%20to%20justify%20your%20foreign%20policy%2C%20it's%20a%20slippery%20slope%20to%20calling%20the%20other%20side%20infidels%20and%20waging%20a%20holy%20war.%20Even%20George%20W.%20Bush%20seemed%20to%20understand%20that%20this%20approach%20wasn't%20a%20good%20idea.%20After%20initially%20framing%20the%20war%20on%20terror%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrusade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20changed%20tack%2C%20condemning%20%26quot%3Bthose%20who%20try%20to%20pit%20religion%20against%20religion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20walking%20through%20the%20Capitol%20interior%20with%20statues%20and%20paintings%20on%20the%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd028090413ab8e1d6f84a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20on%20a%20night-time%20tour%20walked%20through%20the%20interior%20of%20the%20US%20Capitol.%3Cp%3ECheriss%20May%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20won't%20allow%20that%20to%20creep%20into%20the%20consciousness%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Bush%20said.%20Despite%20this%20high-minded%20sentiment%2C%20the%20millions%20who%20died%20as%20a%20result%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwatson.brown.edu%2Fcostsofwar%2Ffiles%2Fcow%2Fimce%2Fpapers%2F2023%2FIndirect%2520Deaths.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBush's%20post-9%2F11%20wars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20by%20the%20estimate%20of%20one%20Brown%20University%20study%2C%20were%20almost%20all%20citizens%20of%20majority-Muslim%20countries.%20But%20Bush's%20generation%20of%20GOP%20leadership%20seemed%20to%20perceive%20some%20risk%20in%20openly%20endorsing%20war%20as%20a%20vehicle%20for%20eradicating%20nonbelievers%2C%20preferring%20instead%20to%20rally%20behind%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20secular%20abstractions.%20They%20felt%20it%20was%20preferable%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20fighting%20%3Cem%3Eagainst%3C%2Fem%3E%20those%20regimes%20that%20use%20religious%20texts%20as%20the%20foundational%20basis%20for%20making%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20times%20change.%20Drollinger's%20Bible%20was%20a%20text%20steeped%20in%20forgiveness%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20grace%2C%20at%20least%20when%20it%20came%20to%20Donald%20Trump's%20behavior.%20But%20then%20there%20were%20the%20non-Trump%20matters%2C%20like%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20women%20could%20ever%20teach%20the%20Bible%20to%20men.%20The%20answer%20was%20as%20rigid%20as%20Revelation's%20prophecies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20pretty%20dogmatic%20about%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20it's%20God's%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20Danielle%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMattathias%20Schwartz%20was%20chief%20national%20security%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aschwartz79%40protonmail.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eschwartz79%40protonmail.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fralph-drollinger-capitol-ministries-trump-advisers-is-ready-for-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709071180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd14286080194819fa5745%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fralph-drollinger-capitol-ministries-trump-advisers-is-ready-for-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ralph%20Drollinger%20has%20spent%20years%20teaching%20his%20brand%20of%