chal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20indicating%20that%20the%20MLAs'%20votes%20are%20split%20evenly%20in%20the%2068-member%20Assembly%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20face%20a%20big%20test%20while%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20Budget%20passed%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20also%20hinted%20that%20the%20party%20will%20move%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20on%20Thursday%20after%20there%20were%20indications%20that%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20three%20independents%20backing%20the%20party%20had%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%2040%20MLAs%20in%20the%2068-member%20Himachal%20Assembly%2C%20was%20expected%20to%20secure%20a%20comfortable%20win%20for%20its%20candidate%2C%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20the%20Congress%20MLAs%20to%20Haryana%2C%20a%20BJP-ruled%20state%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20party's%20preparation%20for%20Wednesday%20and%20the%20no-confidence%20vote.%20The%20BJP%20has%2025%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCounting%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls%20is%20taking%20place%20and%20the%20way%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20threatening%20the%20counting%20officers%20is%20not%20good%20for%20democracy.%20They%20have%20stopped%20counting%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20will%20request%20BJP%20leaders%20to%20remain%20patient%20and%20not%20put%20pressure%20on%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sukhu%20said%20in%20Hindi%20when%20the%20counting%20was%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%205-6%20MLAs%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20a%20convoy%20of%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20and%20the%20CRPF...%20The%20MLAs'%20families%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20them%20and%20the%20legislators%20should%20contact%20them.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20worry.%20There%20is%20a%20government%20and%20an%20opposition%20in%20a%20democracy%20but%20the%20kind%20of%20hooliganism%20(%3Cem%3E'gundagardi'%3C%2Fem%3E)%20being%20done%20by%20the%20opposition%20will%20never%20be%20accepted%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Himachal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%20were%20taken%20to%20Panchkula%20and%20are%20being%20kept%20in%20a%20Public%20Works%20Department%20resthouse%20in%20Sector%201.%20The%20resthouse%20has%20been%20closed%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709057160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fia1am82g_panchkula-pwd-rest-house_625x300_27_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-congress-mlas-from-himachal-taken-to-haryana-alleges-chief-minister-sukhvinder-sukhu-amid-rajya-sabha-poll-battle-5138051%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20the%20BJP%20claimed%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20lost%20majority%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20has%20alleged%20that%20five%20or%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20were%20taken%20to%20Haryana%20accompanied%20by%20a%20convoy%20of%20the%20state's%20police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-congress-mlas-from-himachal-taken-to-haryana-alleges-chief-minister-sukhvinder-sukhu-amid-rajya-sabha-poll-battle-5138051%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-congress-mlas-from-himachal-taken-to-haryana-alleges-chief-minister-sukhvinder-sukhu-amid-rajya-sabha-poll-battle-5138051%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-congress-mlas-from-himachal-taken-to-haryana-alleges-chief-minister-sukhvinder-sukhu-amid-rajya-sabha-poll-battle-5138051%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cross-Voting%2C%20Then%20Some%20Luck%3A%20How%20BJP%20Won%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Poll%20In%20Himachal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20stunning%20upset%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20managed%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20victory%20for%20its%20candidate%20in%20the%20lone%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20despite%20having%20only%2025%20MLAs%20in%20the%2068-member%20Assembly.%20The%20BJP's%20win%20was%20the%20result%20of%20cross-voting%20by%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20a%20draw%20of%20lots%20that%20went%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20loss%20could%20be%20much%20bigger%20than%20just%20a%20blow%20to%20the%20Congress's%20prestige%20as%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20face%20a%20test%20while%20passing%20the%20Budget%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20endangering%20the%20party's%20government%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20-%20one%20of%20only%20three%20states%20that%20it%20rules%20on%20its%20own.%20Compounding%20the%20Congress'%20pain%20will%20be%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20just%20weeks%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20other%20BJP%20MLAs%20met%20Himachal%20Speaker%20Kuldeep%20Singh%20Pathania%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%20and%20demanded%20a%20division%20of%20votes%20for%20passing%20the%20state%20Budget%20instead%20of%20a%20voice%20vote.%20If%20allowed%2C%20the%20division%20of%20votes%20would%20establish%20the%20actual%20support%20of%20each%20party.%20Should%20the%20Congress%20government%20fail%20to%20get%20the%20Budget%20passed%2C%20it%20would%20automatically%20prove%20that%20it%20lacks%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20MLAs%20will%20also%20meet%20Governor%20Shiv%20Pratap%20Shukla%20at%207.30%20am%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeclaring%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20BJP%20candidate%2C%20Harsh%20Mahajan%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Jairam%20Thakur%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BDespite%20having%20such%20a%20huge%20majority%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20lost%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20I%20want%20to%20congratulate%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20BJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%20and%20(Home%20Minister)%20Amit%20Shah.%20We%20have%20pulled%20off%20a%20victory%20when%20our%20chances%20seemed%20very%20low.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%2040%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Assembly%20and%20its%20candidate%2C%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20was%20expected%20to%20win%20comfortably.%20During%20the%20voting%20for%20the%20only%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20for%20which%20elections%20were%20held%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20three%20Independents%20supporting%20the%20government%20reportedly%20cast%20their%20ballots%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Thakur%20-%20who%20was%20also%20the%20Himachal%20chief%20minister%20until%202022%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20lost%20to%20the%20Congress%20-%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20had%20lost%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20Assembly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20move%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20on%20Thursday%20and%20their%20claims%20were%20bolstered%20when%20Mr%20Sukhu%20alleged%20during%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20that%20%26quot%3Bfive%20to%20six%26quot%3B%20Congress%20MLAs%20had%20been%20whisked%20away%20to%20BJP-ruled%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%205-6%20MLAs%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20a%20convoy%20of%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20and%20the%20CRPF...%20The%20MLAs'%20%C2%A0families%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20them%20and%20the%20legislators%20should%20contact%20them.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20worry.%20There%20is%20a%20government%20and%20an%20opposition%20in%20a%20democracy%20but%20the%20kind%20of%20hooliganism%20(%3Cem%3E'gundagardi'%3C%2Fem%3E)%20being%20done%20by%20the%20opposition%20will%20never%20be%20accepted%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Himachal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mahajan%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority.%20%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20is%20in%20the%20minority%20right%20now.%20Fence-sitters%20in%20the%20government%20are%20ready%20to%20come%20to%20this%20side.%20They%20are%20unhappy%20with%20the%20government.%20They%20are%20so%20upset%20that%20they%20can%20do%20anything.%20This%20government%20won't%20go%20on%2C%20it%20will%20topple%20under%20its%20own%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDraw%20Of%20Lots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHelped%20by%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20three%20Independents%20reportedly%20siding%20with%20its%20candidate%2C%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20secure%2034%20ballots%20for%20Mr%20Mahajan%2C%20reducing%20the%20votes%20for%20Mr%20Singhvi%20to%20the%20exact%20same%20number.%20The%20winner%20was%20then%20decided%20through%20a%20draw%20of%20lots%2C%20which%20went%20in%20Mr%20Mahajan's%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20the%20results%20were%20declared%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BAny%20party%20fielding%20a%20candidate%20when%20it%20has%20just%2025%20MLAs%20and%20the%20government%20has%20the%20support%20of%2043%20sends%20out%20only%20one%20message%20-%20that%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20do%20something%20that%20the%20law%20does%20not%20allow.%20And%20I%20am%20not%20talking%20about%20Mr%20Mahajan%20or%20this%20election%20alone%2C%20I%20am%20talking%20about%20the%20principle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20think%20that%20one%20person%2C%20or%20two%20or%20nine%20can%20suddenly%20switch%20ideologies%2C%20then%20I%20think%20all%20of%20us%20live%20in%20a%20fool's%20paradise.%20This%20change%20is%20unfortunate%20for%20India%2C%20and%20especially%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20this%20culture%20did%20not%20exist.%20If%20this%20is%20New%20India%2C%20I%20would%20prefer%20the%20older%20version%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20all%20their%20attempts%2C%20we%20naturally%20reached%20a%20figure%20of%2034%20each.%20This%20is%20probably%20the%20first%20time%20something%20like%20this%20has%20happened%20in%20India%20and%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20happen%20again.%20No%20votes%20were%20declared%20invalid%20and%20there%20were%20no%20second%20preference%20votes.%20The%20winner%20was%20decided%20by%20a%20draw%20of%20lots%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDIA%20Impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20loss%20in%20Himachal%20and%20an%20expected%20defeat%20in%20the%20tenth%20seat%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20come%20as%20a%20setback%20to%20not%20just%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20but%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20as%20a%20whole%20ahead%20of%20the%20all-important%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20At%2080%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20sends%20the%20most%20number%20of%20MLAs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20not%20being%20able%20to%20keep%20its%20flock%20together%20will%20be%20a%20blow%20to%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20just%20days%20after%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20party%20finalised%20a%20seat-sharing%20pact%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20AAP%20for%20Delhi%20and%20four%20other%20states%20has%20also%20been%20worked%20out%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi's%20loss%20in%20Himachal%20may%20hurt%20the%20Congress's%20negotiating%20power%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20finalise%20a%20pact%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20source%20of%20comfort%20for%20the%20party%20in%20an%20otherwise%20dismal%20day%20would%20be%20securing%20its%20expected%20three%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20a%20BJP%20MLA%20cross-voted%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709056800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F8pvpkkjo_harsh-mahajan-bjp_625x300_27_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-claims-victory-in-rajya-sabha-poll-in-himachal-pradesh-after-cross-voting-by-6