www.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fnext-gen-reforms-top-of-agenda-for-govt-s-third-term-fm-sitharaman-124022700876_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fnext-gen-reforms-top-of-agenda-for-govt-s-third-term-fm-sitharaman-124022700876_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fnext-gen-reforms-top-of-agenda-for-govt-s-third-term-fm-sitharaman-124022700876_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alabama's%20legislature%20pushes%20to%20protect%20IVF%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709055629000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F90B5%2Fproduction%2F_132754073_ec277acbe95d57055830ed23dd0485a4c8e66a0c0_0_8192_46101000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68414148%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Republicans%20will%20introduce%20a%20bill%20designed%20to%20protect%20access%2C%20after%20a%20court%20ruling%20cast%20doubt%20on%20its%20availability.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68414148%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68414148.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68414148.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%203%2C%20BJP%201%3A%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Election%20Results%20Out%20For%20Karnataka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Congress%20in%20Karnataka%20won%20three%20seats%20and%20the%20BJP%20one%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Karnataka%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20which%20were%20marred%20by%20cross-voting%20in%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20saffron%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20Maken%2C%20G%20C%20Chandrasekhar%20and%20Syed%20Naseer%20Hussain%2C%20all%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20Narayansa%20K%20Bhandage%20of%20the%20BJP%20got%20elected%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%20in%20the%20polls%20in%20which%20elected%20MLAs%20were%20the%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20candidates%2C%20including%20D%20Kupendra%20Reddy%20of%20the%20JD(S)%20who%20lost%20the%20election%2C%20were%20in%20the%20fray%20for%20the%20four%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20sources%2C%20the%20value%20of%20each%20MLA's%20vote%20is%20100%20and%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20sufficient%20to%20secure%20the%20election%20of%20a%20candidate%20is%204%2C441.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaken%2C%20Hussain%20and%20Bhandage%20got%204%2C700%20votes%20each%20and%20Chandrashekhar%204%2C500.%20Reddy%20got%20only%203%2C600%20votes%20and%20therefore%20did%20not%20make%20the%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLA%20S%20T%20Somashekar%20voted%20for%20Mr%20Maken%2C%20while%20another%20party%20legislator%20A%20Shivaram%20Hebbar%20abstained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20said%20it%20was%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20taking%20legal%20action%20them%20and%20lodging%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Speaker%20U%20T%20Khader%20seeking%20their%20disqualification%20from%20the%20assembly%20for%20violating%20the%20whip%20issued%20to%20them%20to%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20party%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20got%20the%20information%20that%20Somashekar%20has%20done%20cross-voting.%20I%20consulted%20with%20advocate%20Vivek%20Reddy%20who%20is%20our%20state%20legal%20cell%20president%20and%20a%20high%20court%20lawyer.%20We%20will%20ask%20the%20Speaker%20to%20initiate%20action%20(of%20disqualification)%20against%20him%20(Somashekar)%20and%20explore%20the%20possibilities%20to%20take%20steps%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20State%20Assembly%20R%20Ashoka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somashekar%20had%20earlier%20quit%20the%20Congress%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20He%20served%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government%20and%20was%20made%20the%20Mysuru%20district%20in-charge%20minister%20back%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20Mr%20Somashekar%20and%20Mr%20Hebbar%20had%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20increasingly%20began%20identifying%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20(66%20MLAs)%20and%20the%20JD(S)%20(19%20MLAs)%20combined%20had%20fielded%20Kupendra%20Reddy%20though%20they%20did%20not%20have%20the%20requisite%20votes%20to%20get%20him%20elected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20partners%20said%20they%20were%20expecting%20%26quot%3Bconscience%20votes%26quot%3B%2C%20apparently%20from%20the%20rival%20Congress%20camp%2C%20in%20favour%20of%20Mr%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20134%20members%20in%20the%20assembly.%20There%20are%20also%20four%20others%20members%2C%20including%20two%20independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somashekar%20said%20he%20heard%20the%20%26quot%3Bvoice%20of%20his%20conscience%26quot%3B%20and%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20built%20schools%20and%20carried%20out%20developmental%20works%20in%20his%20constituency%26quot%3B.%20Hebbar%20too%20said%20he%20abstained%20from%20voting%20adhering%20to%20his%20conscience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20'atma%20sakshi'%20(conscience)%20but%20'atma%20droha'%20(self%20betrayal)%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20MLC%20N%20Ravi%20Kumar%20said%2C%20commenting%20on%20Somashekar's%20and%20Hebbar's%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20workers%20staged%20a%20demonstration%20in%20Bengaluru%20against%20Mr%20Somashekar.%20Raising%20slogans%2C%20they%20burnt%20his%20effigy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20D%20K%20Shivakumar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20state%20Congress%20chief%2C%20ridiculed%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20JD(S)%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B'Conscience%20vote%20seekers'%20have%20become%20'conscience%20vote%20givers'.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20about%20cross-voting.%20I%20haven't%20seen%20the%20votes%20of%20others%20and%20independents.%20Ask%20the%20BJP%2C%20who%20spoke%20about%20conscience%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20there%20is%20legal%20support%20for%20those%20who%20have%20cast%20conscience%20votes%20to%20Congress%20candidates%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20talk%20about%20it%20when%20it%20happens.%20I%20am%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20complaint%20filed%20with%20the%20Speaker%20regarding%20cross-voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Somashekar%20has%20cast%20his%20vote%20as%20per%20his%20conscience.%20It's%20a%20vote%20against%20the%20unholy%20BJP-JD(S)%20alliance.%20The%20general%20public%2C%20graduates%2C%20and%20teachers%20have%20rejected%20the%20alliance.%20Let's%20see%20what%20the%20legislators%20think.%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20earlier%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20JD(S)%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20party%20had%20sought%20to%20lure%20and%20threaten%20its%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJDS%20needs%2045%20votes%20(for%20their%20candidate)%20to%20win.%20Do%20they%20have%20that%20many%20votes%3F%20Even%20though%20they%20don't%20have%20enough%20votes%2C%20they%20still%20fielded%20the%20candidate%20and%20are%20luring%20our%20MLAs.%20Do%20they%20have%20a%20conscience%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%20regarding%20the%20threat%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Siddaramaiah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20here%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20JD(S)%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20JD(S)%20does%20not%20have%20'atma'%20(soul)%2C%20how%20can%20it%20have%20'atma%20sakshi'%20(conscience)%3F%20They%20call%20themselves%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20but%20whom%20did%20they%20join%20with%3F%26quot%3B.%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20JD(S)%20forming%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20and%20JD(S)%20second-in-command%20H%20D%20Kumaraswamy%20said%20the%20FIR%20against%20Kupendra%20Reddy%20and%20his%20aides%20was%20registered%20at%20Vidhana%20Soudha%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumaraswamy%20said%20the%20complainant%20MLA%20did%20not%20say%20that%20he%20was%20lured%2C%20but%20that%20some%20other%20MLAs%20were%20%26quot%3Bapproached%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMelukote%20MLA%20Darshan%20Puttannaiah%20of%20Karnataka%20Sarvodaya%20Paksha%20too%20had%20said%20that%20it's%20true%20that%20his%20vote%20was%20sought%20but%20no%20one%20had%20lured%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20JD(S)%20state%20chief%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumaraswamy%20said%20the%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20had%20decided%20to%20field%20Kupendra%20Reddy%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20votes%20of%20the%2019%20JD(S)%20MLAs%20and%20the%20additional%20BJP%20votes%20after%20its%20first%20preferential%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709055360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fa3djrgko_rs_625x300_27_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-wins-three-seat-bjp-one-in-karnataka-rajya-sabha-elections-5137921%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ruling%20Congress%20in%20Karnataka%20won%20three%20seats%20and%20the%20BJP%20one%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Karnataka%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-wins-three-seat-bjp-one-in-karnataka-rajya-sabha-elections-5137921%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-wins-three-seat-bjp-one-in-karnataka-rajya-sabha-elections-5137921%2Famp%2F1%22