e%22%3A%22Amended%20Citizenship%20Rules%20Likely%20To%20Be%20Enforced%20From%20Next%20Month%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20contentious%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20which%20gives%20citizenship%20to%20religious%20minorities%20from%20three%20neighbouring%20countries%20who%20settled%20in%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20next%20month%20--%20four%20years%20after%20it%20was%20passed%20--%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%20Sources%20said%20the%20online%20portal%20is%20ready%20for%20registrations%20and%20dry%20runs%20have%20already%20been%20done%20by%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20applies%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%20and%20Christians%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20and%20will%20be%20implemented%20before%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20the%20general%20elections%20comes%20into%20play.%20The%20timing%20is%20crucial%2C%20given%20the%20approaching%20election.%20Non-implementation%20of%20the%20law%20would%20have%20caused%20it%20to%20lapse.%20The%20time%20window%20extended%20till%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20was%20a%20key%20electoral%20agenda%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Bengal%2C%20where%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20was%20opposed%20to%20it.%20In%20December%20last%20year%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20declared%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20cannot%20be%20halted%20as%20it%20is%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20move%20has%20been%20made%20to%20capitalise%20on%20majority%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20CAA%20will%20help%20refugees%20from%20these%20neighbouring%20countries%20who%20don't%20have%20documents.%20The%20maximum%20number%20of%20applications%20for%20long-term%20visas%20which%20the%20ministry%20received%20was%20from%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPowers%20to%20grant%20long-term%20visas%C2%A0%20--%20seen%20as%20the%20precursor%20to%20CAA%20--%20have%20been%20given%20to%20district%20authorities%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20over%2030%20District%20Magistrates%20and%20Home%20Secretaries%20of%20nine%20states%20were%20given%20powers%20to%20grant%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%2C%20Parsis%20and%20Christians%20coming%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%201955.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20annual%20report%20of%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%2C%20from%20April%201%2C%202021%20to%20December%2031%2C%202021%2C%20a%20total%20of%201%2C414%20non-Muslim%20minorities%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20were%20given%20Indian%20citizenship%20by%20registration%20or%20naturalization%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%201955.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20--%20passed%20in%202019%20amid%20massive%20protests%20across%20the%20country%20--%20made%20religion%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20test%20of%20Indian%20citizenship.%20The%20government%20contended%20that%20it%20would%20help%20non-Muslim%20refugees%20from%20three%20Muslim-dominated%20neighbouring%20countries%20if%20they%20fled%20to%20India%20because%20of%20religious%20persecution.%3Cbr%3E%5CnCritics%20said%20the%20law%20discriminates%20against%20Muslims%20and%20violates%20secular%20tenets%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaken%20together%2C%20the%20CAA%2C%20NRC%20and%20the%20NPR%20unleashed%20a%20storm%20of%20protests%20across%20the%20country%20in%202019%2C%20before%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20put%20it%20all%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20protests%20wound%20up%2C%20the%20National%20Registry%20of%20Citizens%2C%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20rolled%20out%20across%20the%20country%2C%20was%20put%20on%20hold%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709049840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-11%2Fng1kg2vo_delhi-generic-afp_625x300_12_November_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frules-to-fast-track-citizenship-of-minorities-from-3-nations-likely-to-be-enforced-next-month-sources-5137451%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20contentious%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20which%20will%20give%20citizenship%20to%20religious%20minorities%20from%20three%20neighbouring%20countries%20--%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20--%20who%20settled%20in%20India%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20implemented%20from%20next%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frules-to-fast-track-citizenship-of-minorities-from-3-nations-likely-to-be-enforced-next-month-sources-5137451%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frules-to-fast-track-citizenship-of-minorities-from-3-nations-likely-to-be-enforced-next-month-sources-5137451%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frules-to-fast-track-citizenship-of-minorities-from-3-nations-likely-to-be-enforced-next-month-sources-5137451%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dutch%20mega-trial%20exposes%20brutal%20gangland%20underworld%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709049486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F15E73%2Fproduction%2F_132751798_gettyimages-1241172001.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68416287%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Key%20figures%20in%20a%20powerful%20Dutch%20drug%20cartel%20are%20handed%20life%20sentences%20after%20a%20near%20six-year%20saga.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A68%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68416287%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68416287.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68416287.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'3%20Idiots'%20co-stars%20Aamir%20Khan-Sharman%20Joshi%20reunite%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709048559000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108050009%2Cimgsize-77124.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2F3-idiots-co-stars-aamir-khan-and-sharman-joshi-aka-rancho-and-raju-reunite-at-kiran-raos-laapataa-ladies-screening-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F108050009.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108050009.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAamir%20Khan's%20'3%20Idiots'%20co-star%20Sharman%20Joshi%20attended%20the%20special%20screening%20of%20Kiran%20Rao's%20film%20'Laapataa%20Ladies'%20in%20Mumbai.%20They%20twinned%20in%20spectacles%20and%20struck%20poses.%20Aamir%2C%20R%20Madhavan%20and%20Sharman%20promoted%20Sharman's%20film%20'Congratulations'%20in%20matching%20tracksuits%20and%20a%20group%20hug.%20Fans%20were%20delighted%20to%20see%20the%20trio.%20Sharman%20shared%20a%20video.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2F3-idiots-co-stars-aamir-khan-and-sharman-joshi-aka-rancho-and-raju-reunite-at-kiran-raos-laapataa-ladies-screening-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F108050009.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kishan%20Flops%20On%20Finally%20Returning%20To%20Action%2C%20Dismissed%20By%20Maxwell%20For...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20star%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20wicketkeeper-batter%2C%20finally%20made%20a%20return%20to%20competitive%20cricket%20at%20the%20DY%20Patil%20T20%20Cup%20on%20Tuesday.%20Ishan%20Kishan's%20absence%20from%20competitive%20cricket%20made%20big%20news%20since%20he%20opted%20for%20a%20break%20midway%20into%20India's%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20was%20ignored%20for%20the%20home%20T20%20series%20against%20Afghanistan%20and%20the%20Test%20series%20against%20England.%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20has%20to%20play%20some%20form%20of%20cricket%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%20to%20the%20national%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20missed%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20and%20instead%20chose%20to%20train%20with%20his%20IPL%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E.%20he%20even%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20his%20gym%20session%20with%20Hardik%20Pandya.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20was%20finally%20seen%20in%20action%20for%C2%A0Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20team%20against%20Route%20Mobile%20Limited%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai.%C2%A0Kishan%20kept%20the%20wickets%20for%20RBI%20as%20his%20team%20fielded%20first%20following%20Route%20Mobile's%20decision%20to%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4NVlYFIV60%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4NVlYFIV60%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20World%20Cricket%20Live%20(%40world_cric_live)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fworld_cric_live%2Fstatus%2F1762461284216476074%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20return%2C%20Kishan%20played%20a%20part%20in%20one%20dismissal%20as%20he%20stumped%20Sumit%20Dhekale%20off%20Sayan%20Mondal%20at%20the%20DY%20Patil%20University%20Ground.%20Then%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20he%20entertained%20for%20a%20bit%20as%20he%20made%2019%20off%2012%20balls%20with%20two%20boundaries%20and%20a%20six.%C2%A0Kishan%20was%20dismissed%20while%20trying%20to%20hit%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Maxwell%20Swaminathan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F115389-maxwell-swaminathan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMaxwell%20Swaminathan%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20mid-off.%20RBI%20were%20chasing%20a%20target%20of%20193%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%20fell%20in%C2%A0%20the%20fourth%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoute%20batted%20first%20and%20posted%20192%20for%20eight%20in%20their%2020%20overs%20thanks%20to%20Aayush%20Vartan's%2054%20off%2031%20balls%20with%20five%20boundaries%20and%20three%20sixes.%20Dhekale%20made%2042%20off%20just%2017%20balls%20with%20one%20boundary%20and%20five%20sixes.%20In%20their%20response%20RBI%20self-destructed%20as%20they%20were%20shot%20out%20for%20just%20103%20in%2016.3%20overs.%20For%20Route%20the%20best%20bowler%20was%20Badrey%20Alam%20(5-20).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20BCCI%20Secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20made%20it%20clear%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20all%20centrally%20contracted%20cricketers%20will%20have%20to%20mandatorily%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%20and%20the%20management%20will%20not%20tolerate%20any%20kind%20of%20excuses%20in%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20interacting%20with%20the%20reporters%20at%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20renaming%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Saurashtra%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%2C%20Shah%20pointed%20out%20that%20all%20players%20will%20have%20to%20represent%20their%20state%20teams%20if%20called%20upon%20by%20coach%20or%20captain.%20The%20statement%20came%20amidst%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20reports%20that%20suggest%20that%20BCCI%20has%20asked%20him%20to%20play%20for%20Jharkhand%20in%20Ranji%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20mentioned%20Kishan%20during%20the%20interaction%20but%20quickly%20added%20that%20the%20announcement%20was%20not%20targeted%20towards%20him%20and%20this%20rule%20will%20apply%20for%20all%20cricketers%20who%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20national%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20contracted%20players%20have%20been%20told%20on%20phone%20and%20I'll%20be%20writing%20to%20them%20too.%20If%20chairman%20of%20selectors%2C%20coach%20%26amp%3B%20captain%20want%20you%20to%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%20then%20you%20gotta%20play.%20'Nakhre%20Nahi%20Chalenge'%20(no%20tantrums).%20And%20as%20far%20as%20Ishan%20Kishan%20is%20concerned%2C%20he%20is%20young%2C%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20this%20specifically%20about%20him%20as%20it%20will%20be%20applicable%20for%20all%20the%20players%20uniformly%2C%26quot%3B%20Jay%20Shah%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20will%20have%20to%20play%2C%20otherwise%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%20has%20given%20me%20his%20suggestions%20and%20I%20am%20going%20to%20give%20him%20a%20free%20hand%20to%20let%20him%20take%20his%20own%20calls%20freely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709048280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fucs8pjmg_ishan-kishan_625x300_27_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fishan-kishan-flops-on-finally-returning-to-action-gets-dismissed-by-maxwell-for-watch-5138344%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ishan%20Kishan's%20absence%20from%20competitive%20cricket%20made%20big%20news%20since%20he%20opted%20for%20a%20break%20midway%20into%20India's%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Facing%20Fire%2C%20TMC%20Leaders%20Say%20Allegiance%20Only%20to%20People%20of%20Bengal%2C%20Shahjahan%20Arrest%20Soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27210539%2FTrinamool-press.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Facing%20fire%20for%20inaction%20against%20local%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20leaders%20in%20light%20of%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20land%20grab%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20said%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2027)%20that%20the%20state%20government%20is%20taking%20action%20and%20the%20key%20accused%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20will%20be%20arrested%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Saket%20Gokhale%20as%20well%20as%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs-elect%20Sagarika%20Ghose%20and%20Sushmita%20Dev%20said%20the%20state%20government%20has%20already%20arrested%2020%20people%20and%20that%20Shahjahan%20will%20also%20be%20arrested%20now%20that%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20has%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20stay%20on%20taking%20action%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20West%20Bengal%20police%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20partisan%20and%20acting%20on%20Mamata%20%5BBanerjee%5D%E2%80%99s%20instructions.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20BJP%20that%20the%20advocate%20general%20has%20informed%20the%20court%20that%2020%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20are%20accusing%20the%20West%20Bengal%20police%20of%20being%20partisan%2C%20we%20want%20to%20ask%20them%2C%20who%20is%20Shibu%20Hazra%3F%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20proved%20that%20whether%20it%20is%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20mothers%2C%20sisters%20or%20elderly%2C%20if%20there%20is%20any%20injustice%2C%20she%20will%20take%20action%20and%20not%20look%20at%20any%20party%20affiliation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHazra%2C%20a%20TMC%20block-level%20president%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20zilla%20parishad%2C%20was%20named%20by%20multiple%20women%20in%20serious%20sexual%20harassment%20cases%20and%20was%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fsandeshkhali-unrest-as-women-led-protests-escalate-tmcs-outsider-claims-find-little-resonance%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month%20after%20the%20state%20government%20faced%20pressure%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20including%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20question%20by%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fi%3Eon%20why%20the%20state%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20act%20against%20Shahjahan%20despite%20allegations%20of%20land-grab%20and%20attacks%20on%20women%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20as%20far%20back%20as%20in%202012%2C%20the%20TMC%20leaders%20said%20that%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20had%20not%20been%20filed%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20file%20a%20complaint%20if%20there%20is%20an%20FIR.%20Tomorrow%2C%20I%20can%20stand%20and%20say%20something%20in%20front%20of%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%2C%20but%20the%20police%20will%20investigate%20only%20when%20an%20FIR%20is%20filed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gokhale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20by%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fi%3Eabout%20why%20the%20issue%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20assembly%20did%20not%20warrant%20any%20action%2C%20Ghose%20added%20that%20now%20that%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%2C%20the%20police%20investigation%20has%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20FIRs%20have%20come%2C%20the%20police%20are%20investigating%20and%20arresting%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%3Ci%3E%20The%20Telegraph%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fsandeshkhali-alert-in-records-former-cpm-mla-nirapada-sardar-took-up-atrocities-10-years-ago-in-house%2Fcid%2F2002964%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20official%20assembly%20records%20that%20CPI(M)%20MLA%20Nirapada%20Sardar%2C%20who%20represented%20Sandeshkhali%20from%202011%20to%202016%2C%20had%20raised%20those%20issues%20at%20least%20thrice%20%E2%80%93%20twice%20in%202012%20and%20once%20in%202013%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESardar%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20February%2011%20on%20charges%20of%20fomenting%20trouble%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20was%20granted%20bail%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20proactively%20engaging%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20issues%20across%20the%20state.%20In%20every%20area%2C%20the%20TMC%20government%20is%20looking%20to%20address%20grievances%20that%20are%20brought%20by%20the%20women%20of%20the%20area%20and%20when%20the%20complaint%20was%20registered%2C%20the%20government%20did%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghose%20to%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGokhale%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20had%20not%20acted%20against%20Shahjahan%20due%20to%20a%20February%207%20order%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20restraining%20any%20action%20against%20him.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20take%20aim%20at%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20February%207%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20in%20its%20order%20clearly%20restrained%20West%20Bengal%20police%20from%20taking%20any%20action%20against%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%20February%208%20onwards%20every%20single%20day%2C%20one%20BJP%20minister%2C%20one%20BJP%20MLA%2C%20somebody%20from%20this%20commission%20or%20that%20commission%20started%20visiting%20Sandeshkhali%20every%20single%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYesterday%20%5BFebruary%2027%5D%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20issued%20a%20clarification%20that%20the%20West%20Bengal%20police%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsandeshkhali-updates-tmc-sheikh-shahjahan%5C%22%3Efree%20to%20take%20action%20against%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20happened%20at%2012%3A30%20in%20the%20afternoon%20%5Band%5D%20by%201-1%3A30%20pm%2C%20an%20FIR%20had%20been%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20West%20Bengal%20police%20are%20very%20confident%20that%20they%20will%20nab%20him%20in%20a%20few%20days.%20This%20is%20not%20Nirav%20Modi%20or%20Mehul%20Choksi%2C%20where%20they%20take%20a%20foreign%20passport%20and%20leave%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20BJP%20government%20but%20a%20TMC%20government.%20He%20will%20be%20brought%20to%20book%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan%20has%20been%20absconding%20since%20January%205%2C%20when%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officials%20who%20were%20investigating%20an%20alleged%20ration%20distribution%20scam%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bengals-sandeshkhali-controversial-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahans-hold-is-powerful%5C%22%3Eattacked%20at%20his%20residence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDev%20said%20that%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20will%20be%20visiting%20Sandeshkhali%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20%5Bthe%20BJP%5D%20did%20not%20remove%20Brij%20Bhushan%20%5BSharan%20Singh%5D%2C%20you%20garlanded%20Bilkis%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20rapists.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20them%20that%20her%20%5BBanerjee%E2%80%99s%5D%20only%20allegiance%20is%20the%20people%20of%20Bengal%20and%20those%20who%20do%20injustice%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Bengal%20will%20face%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20assure%20you%20Mamata%20Baner