ynastic%20(politics)%20and%20started%20the%20tradition%20of%20good%20governance.%20He%20worked%20for%20quality%20education%20and%20healthcare%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20women%20respected%20him%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20the%20way%20the%20DMK%20has%20been%20working%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20MGR%20Sahib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMGR%20was%20a%20true%20leader.%20Today%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20way%20the%20DMK%20has%20been%20working%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20MGR%20Sahib.%20If%20there%20was%20someone%20after%20MGR%20who%20worked%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20development%20and%20prosperity%2C%20it%20was%20Amma%20Jayalalithaa%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20he%20has%20an%20emotional%20connection%20with%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20recalled%20the%20installation%20of%20'Sengol'%20as%20a%20move%20to%20respect%20the%20grand%20heritage%20of%20the%20country%20and%20TN%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20Tamil%20language%20and%20culture%20has%20been%20extremely%20special.%20The%20Tamil%20poem%20I%20read%20at%20the%20UN%20is%20being%20discussed%20globally.%20In%20my%20constituency%2C%20Varanasi%2C%20I%20organised%20the%20Kashi%20Tamil%20Sangamam.%20Respecting%20the%20great%20tradition%20of%20our%20country%20and%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20I%20got%20the%20'Sengol'%20installed%20in%20the%20Parliament%20on%20the%20highest%20pedestal.%20After%20this%2C%20the%20whole%20country%20has%20a%20new%20curiosity%20to%20know%20more%20about%20Tamil%20Nadu...%20The%20soil%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20given%20me%20immense%20love%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNearly%2032%20years%20ago%2C%20in%201991%2C%20when%20I%20kickstarted%20the%20Ekta%20Yatra%2C%20it%20was%20started%20from%20Kanyakumari.%20That%20yatra%20was%20started%20to%20fulfil%20two%20objectives-%20one%20was%20to%20unfurl%20the%20Indian%20tricolour%20at%20the%20Lal%20Chowk%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20and%20the%20second%20was%20to%20abrogate%20Article%20370...%20Today%2C%20both%20of%20these%20tasks%20have%20been%20successfully%20completed.%20And%20now%2C%20'en%20man%20en%20makkal'%20padayatra%20is%20taking%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20a%20new%20path%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20urged%20all%20the%20BJP%20karyakartas%20to%20best%20serve%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20urge%20all%20the%20BJP%20karyakartas%20to%20best%20serve%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20You%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20BJP's%20Sankalp%20of%20third-term%20reaches%20each%20and%20every%20household%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Your%20bright%20future%20is%20Modi's%20guarantee.%20You%20must%20remember%20that%20Modi%20is%20always%20with%20you!%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20those%20who%20make%20political%20equations%20should%20note%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20deciding%20India's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20given%20more%20funds%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20than%20in%20the%20past.%20When%20Modi%20works%2C%20he%20works%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20is%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20the%20southern%20states%20of%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709046060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fm1phbfa8_pm-modi-in-varanasi_625x300_23_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fway-dmk-has-been-working-in-tamil-nadu-an-insult-to-mgr-sahib-pm-modi-5137586%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Invoking%20the%