5e4b0189a6a7f0197%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Falabama-mercedes-united-auto-workers_n_65dd0ad5e4b0189a6a7f0197%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Directs%20AIIMS%20to%20Appoint%20Board%20for%20Medical%20Examination%20of%20NewsClick's%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F26113950%2Fprab.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2027)%20has%20instructed%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%2C%20Delhi%20to%20hold%20an%20independent%20medical%20examination%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fnewsclick-supreme-court-directs-aiims-independent-medical-examination-prabir-purkayastha%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20board%20consisting%20of%20specialist%20medical%20officer%2C%20central%20jail%20Tihar%20is%20received.%20It%20is%20submitted%20that%20the%20report%20does%20not%20show%20the%20true%20medical%20condition%20of%20the%20petitioner.%20It%20is%20submitted%20that%20the%20record%20will%20reveal%20the%20report%20is%20not%20correct%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20apex%20court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B.R.%20Gavai%20and%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CTaking%20into%20consideration%20all%20this%2C%20it%20will%20be%20appropriate%20that%20the%20medical%20condition%20is%20examined%20by%20a%20board%20appointed%20by%20the%20AIIMS%20director.%20The%20board%20shall%20also%20consider%20the%20jail%20records%20%5Band%20the%5D%20complete%20medical%20history%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20petitioner.%20List%20after%20two%20weeks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERejecting%20the%20argument%20of%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20founder%20was%20asking%20for%20special%20treatment%2C%20the%20bench%20underlined%20that%20if%20Asaram%20Bapu%20could%20get%20medical%20treatment%20at%20AIIMS%2C%20then%20Purkayastha%20could%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fweeks-after-unprecedented-raids-newsclick-staffers-grapple-with-waiting-game%5C%22%3ENewsClick%3A%20Govt%20Impunity%20Caused%20Seizure%20of%20as%20Many%20as%20250%20Devices%2C%20Paralysing%20Work%20of%2090%20Journalists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20convict%20in%20Jodhpur%20(Asaram)%20who%20keeps%20getting%20medical%20treatment%20at%20AIIMS%20%E2%80%A6%20you%20can%20release%20him%20and%20then%20he%20can%20get%20treated%20wherever%20he%20wants%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judges%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20Sibal%2C%20appearing%20for%20Purkayastha%2C%20highlighted%20in%20the%20court%20that%20his%20client%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20not%20pass%20away%20while%20they%20%5Bthe%20additional%20solicitor%20genera%5D%20keep%20asking%20for%20pass%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20medical%20report%20does%20not%20show%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20jail%20%5Band%5D%20jail%20records%20must%20be%20called%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20heard%20the%20matter%20as%20Purkayastha%20filed%20a%20plea%20challenging%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20upholding%20a%20trial%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20remand%20him%20and%20others%20in%20the%20case%20to%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca