rther%20south%20to%20overcrowded%20Rafah.%20Some%201.5%20million%20Palestinians%20are%20sheltering%20in%20the%20city%2C%20which%20remains%20a%20focus%20of%20international%20concern%20amid%20the%20threat%20of%20an%20all-out%20Israeli%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIncreased%20airstrikes%20in%20Rafah%2C%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Eincluding%20in%20residential%20areas%20without%20prior%20warnings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0have%20heightened%20fears%20that%20they%20will%20further%20hamper%20overstretched%20humanitarian%20operations%2C%E2%80%9D%20UNRWA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20people%20have%20been%20moving%20out%20of%20Rafah%20towards%20Deir%20Al%20Balah%20and%20Nuseirat%20refugee%20camps%20in%20the%20Middle%20Area%20of%20Gaza%2C%20even%20though%20there%20are%20reports%20of%20further%20fighting%20and%20airstrikes%20in%20those%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumanitarian%20update%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2075%25%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20up%20to%201.7%20million%20people%2C%20have%20been%20displaced%20since%20the%20start%20of%20hostilities%20following%20the%20brutal%20Hamas-led%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20on%207%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20agencies%20continue%20to%20warn%20of%20the%20deepening%20hunger%20crisis%20in%20Gaza.%20More%20than%20two%20million%20people%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fhostilities-gaza-strip-and-israel-reported-impact-day-142%3F_gl%3D1*j84z3i*_ga*MTM3MDIwNjc4My4xNjQ0NTI0NDM4*_ga_E60ZNX2F68*MTcwODk2MzkyMy4xNDUuMS4xNzA4OTY0NDcxLjIxLjAuMA..%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eare%20facing%20crisis%20or%20worse%20levels%20of%20food%20insecurity%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20humanitarian%20affairs%20office%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unocha.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOCHA%3C%2Fa%3E