d.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnot-looking-to-acquire-stake-in-indian-carriers-at-present-says-airasia-124022700915_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Across%20Assam%2C%20Hindutva%20Group's%20Posters%20Issue%20'Final%20Warnings'%20to%20Christian%20Institutions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27181706%2FUntitled-design-2-6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20a%20recent%20call%20by%20a%20Hindutva%20group%2C%20Sanmilita%20Sanatan%20Samaj%2C%20to%20avoid%20all%20religious%20symbols%20and%20costumes%20in%20educational%20institutions%20in%20Assam%2C%20a%20number%20of%20top%20Christian%20institutions%20across%20the%20northeastern%20state%20have%20seen%20posters%20stuck%20on%20their%20premises%2C%20warning%20them%20against%20using%20their%20schools%20as%20religious%20institutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20posters%2C%20printed%20by%20the%20group%20in%20Assamese%2C%20have%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20final%20warning%20to%20stop%20using%20the%20school%20as%20a%20religious%20institution%E2%80%A6stop%20anti-Bharat%20and%20unconstitutional%20activities%20or%20else%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minority%20institutions%20were%20asked%20to%20%E2%80%9Cremove%E2%80%9D%20churches%20from%20within%20their%20school%20premises%2C%20along%20with%20all%20idols%20of%20Jesus%20and%20Mary.%20The%20posters%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CChristian%20missionary%20educational%20institutions%20should%20stop%20ignoring%20the%20proposed%20New%20Education%20Policy%20(of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government)%20and%20show%20respect%20to%20the%20Indian%20Parliament.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2018%2C%20authorities%20at%20the%20well-known%20Carmel%20School%20in%20Jorhat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fnorth-east%2Fassam-christian-school-faces-statue-threat-seeks-police-protection%2Fcid%2F2001270%5C%22%3Eapproached%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20local%20police%20after%20spotting%20such%20a%20poster%20on%20its%20boundary%20wall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20application%2C%20written%20by%20school%20principal%20Sister%20Rose%20Fatima%2C%20said%20that%20her%20institution%20had%20%E2%80%98been%20very%20accommodating%20and%20respectful%20towards%20people%20of%20every%20religion%20and%20culture%E2%80%99%20and%20maintained%20an%20%E2%80%98atmosphere%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquility%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20reported%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20news%20report%20said%20that%20the%20police%20station%20had%20confirmed%20the%20development%20and%20was%20investigating%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemeghalayan.com%2Fanother-hindu-radical-group-launches-poster-campaign-against-christian-schools-across-assam%2F%5C%22%3Eposters%20were%20spotted%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Don%20Bosco%20Boys%20School%20and%20Saint%20Mary%E2%80%99s%20School%20in%20Guwahati%20and%20other%20Christian%20minority%20schools%20in%20Barpeta%2C%20Dibrugarh%20and%20Sivasagar%20towns.%20Posters%20were%20signed%20in%20Guwahati%E2%80%99s%20busy%20Dighalipukhuri%20area%20and%20Nehru%20Park%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20the%20poster%20campaign%20by%20the%20Guwahati-based%20outfit%20begun%20after%20it%20asked%20Christian%20missionary-run%20schools%20on%20February%207%20to%20remove%20all%20religious%20symbols%20and%20statues%20from%20their%20premises%20within%2015%20days.%20A%20similar%20diktat%20was%20issued%20by%20another%20group%2C%20Kutumba%20Suraksha%20Parishad%2C%20recently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20against%20the%20Christians.%20But%20we%20are%20against%20the%20subtle%20use%20of%20religious%20symbols%20aimed%20at%20conversion.%20The%20missionary%20schools%20focus%20on%20propagating%20Christianity%2C%20not%20India%20or%20Indian%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Sanmilita%20Sanatan%20Samaj%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fassam-hindu-group-starts-poster-campaign-against-missionary-schools%2Farticle67881789.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CWe%2520are%2520not%2520against%2520the%2Cmember%2520of%2520the%2520group%2520said%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Assam%20Christian%20Forum%20has%20termed%20these%20posters%20an%20act%20by%20%E2%80%9Cfringe%20elements%E2%80%9D%20but%20has%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20institutions%20have%20alerted%20the%20state%20director%20general%20of%20police%20and%20the%20relevant%20district%20police%20chiefs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20institutions%20have%20always%20respected%20and%20accommodated%20individuals%20of%20all%20religions%20and%20cultures%2C%20maintaining%20a%20peaceful%20and%20tranquil%20atmosphere.%20Had%20conversion%20been%20our%20goal%2C%20at%20least%20half%20of%20Assam%20would%20have%20been%20Christians%20by%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Forum%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20about%20400%20such%20educational%20institutions%20runs%20by%20Christian%20missionaries%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHimanta%E2%80%99s%20comments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20poster%20campaign%20by%20the%20Hindutva%20groups%20has%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20has%20equated%20magical%20healing%20with%20proselytisation%20by%20Christian%20missionaries.%20BJP%20government%20in%20Assam%20has%20tabled%20a%20controversial%20bill%20in%20the%20assembly.%20Named%20Assam%20(Healing)%20Prevention%20of%20Evil%20Practices%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20the%20proposed%20law%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20assembly%20on%20February%2021.%20CM%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20thereafter%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20Bill%20would%20stop%20all%20healing%20practices%20which%20are%20carried%20out%20by%20some%20with%20an%20ulterior%20motive%20in%20the%20state%2C%20leading%20the%20Assam%20Christian%20Forum%20to%20call%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmisguided%20and%20misleading%E2%80%9D%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHealing%2C%20in%20our%20context%2C%20is%20not%20synonymous%20with%20proselytisation.%20It%20is%20a%20compassionate%20response%20to%20human%20suffering%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religious%20affiliations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20forum%20said%2C%20insisting%20that%20labelling%20prayer%20as%20magical%20healing%20oversimplifies%20the%20profound%20spiritual%20dimensions%20of%20faith%20and%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20has%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnenews.in%2Fnagaland%2Fnagaland-baptist-church-council-denounces-assam-healing-bill-2024-as-insensitive%2F7438%2F%5C%22%3Ecriticised%20by%20Nagaland%20Baptist%20Church%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Council%20has%20termed%20it%20a%20manifestation%20of%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20bigotry%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinsensitive%20act%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709039751000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27181706%2FUntitled-design-2-6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindutva-group-assam-christian-institutions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20posters%2C%20printed%20by%20the%20Sammilata%20Sanatan%20Samaj%20group%20in%20Assamese%2C%20have%20said%2C%20'This%20is%20the%20final%20warning%20to%20stop%20using%20the%20school%20as%20a%20religious%20institution%E2%80%A6stop%20anti-Bharat%20and%20unconstitutional%20activities%20or%20else%E2%80%A6'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindutva-group-assam-christian-institutions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20AAP-Congress%20Alliance%20Is%20Good%20Optics%2C%20But%20It%20Can%20Confuse%20Voters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvu8dmsjo_arvind-kejriwal-rahul-gandhi-rahul-kejriwal-650_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20week%20of%20good%20news%20for%20supporters%20of%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%20after%20a%20series%20of%20setbacks%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Bihar.%20Last%20week%2C%20after%20sealing%20the%20deal%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-bjp-should-not-ignore-sp-congress-alliance-5111410%5C%22%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Congress%20finalised%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Faap-congress-alliance-can-inject-dynamism-into-the-poll-landscape-5130327%5C%22%3Eseat-sharing%20pact%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%20(AAP)%20in%20five%20states%20%2F%20Union%20Territories%20covering%2046%20seats.%20The%20Congress%2C%20whose%20governments%20were%20dislodged%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20by%20the%20AAP%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-delhi-aap-congress-seal-seat-deal-for-goa-haryana-gujarat-sources-5105903%5C%22%3Ehas%20accommodated%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20party%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20put%20up%20a%20united%20front%20against%20the%20BJP%20juggernaut%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hopes%20of%20an%20AAP-INC%20alliance%20materialising%20in%20Delhi%20were%20initially%20dashed%20after%20the%20two%20parties%20decided%20to%20contest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHTaXOFL4veY%5C%22%3Eseparately%20in%20Punjab%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20to%20give%20credit%20to%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20two%20parties%2C%20they%20finally%20found%20their%20way%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fmy-ethics-won-t-allow-aap-haryana-leader-quits-over-congress-tie-up-754479%5C%22%3Ethrough%20tough%3C%2Fa%3E%20seat-sharing%20talks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ECongress%20Willing%20To%20'Accommodate'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20displayed%20a%20bigger%20heart%2C%20which%20many%20analysts%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months%20have%20accused%20it%20of%20lacking.%20It%20has%20accepted%20a%20smaller%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20-%20three%20-%20despite%20having%20received%20a%20higher%20vote%20share%20in%20the%202019%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-announces-lok-sabha-election-candidates-for-delhi-and-haryana-5136964%5C%22%3EHaryana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20has%20conceded%20one%20seat%20to%20the%20AAP%2C%20where%20it%20has%20a%20limited%20presence%2C%20and%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20it%20has%20given%20away%20two%20seats.%20The%20AAP%20had%20made%20a%20scintillating%20debut%20in%20Gujarat%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20polls%2C%20bagging%20a%2013%25%20vote%20share%20and%20helping%20the%20BJP%20secure%20a%20record%20victory%20of%20150-plus%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-aap-finalises-seat-sharing-for-delhi-agree-to-a-four-three-split-5117634%5C%22%3EGoa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20AAP%20will%20support%20the%20Congress%20despite%20its%20decent%20presence.%20It's%20the%20same%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20where%20the%20AAP%20now%20has%20a%20Mayor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20has%20faced%20some%20opposition%20from%20the%20Congress's%20local%20leadership%20in%20states.%20The%20party%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20almost%20zero%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20since%20the%20AAP's%20rise%2C%20and%20has%20lost%20around%2035%25%20votes%20since%202008.%20The%20AAP's%20share%20of%20over%2050%25%20has%20largely%20come%20from%20the%20Congress's%2070%25%20and%20other%20parties'%2030%25%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EAAP%20Has%20Grown%20At%20Congress's%20Expense%20In%20Punjab%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Delhi%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Punjab%2C%20the%20Congress's%20vote%20share%20has%20dropped%20from%2040%25%20in%202012%20to%2023%25%20in%202022.%20The%20Akali%20Dal's%20share%20dropped%20from%2035%25%20to%2019%25%20during%20the%20same%20period.%20The%20AAP%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20having%20made%20a%20dent%20in%20both%20these%20parties'%20voting%20segments%2C%20currently%20commands%20a%2042%25%20vote%20share%2C%20with%20which%20it%20swept%20the%20state%20in%202022%20winning%2092%20of%20the%20total%20117%20seats.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20vote%20share%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20stayed%20unaffected%20at%20around%207%25%20during%20this%20period.%20Ultimately%20though%2C%20no%20deal%20has%20been%20finalised%20for%20Punjab%2C%20with%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%20contesting%20independently%20for%20its%2013%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20Congress%20got%20a%2027%25%20vote%20share%20in%202022%2C%2015%20percentage%20points%20less%20than%20in%202017.%20All%20of%20this%20was%20bagged%20by%20the%20AAP%2C%20which%20in%20a%20debut%20of%20sorts%20ended%20up%20bagging%20a%2013%25%20vote%20share.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20effect%2C%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20have%20made%20peace%20with%20a%20party%20that%20has%20grown%20at%20its%20own%20expense%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Gujarat.%20The%20AAP's%20presence%20has%20helped%20the%20BJP%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Goa%20to%20some%20extent.%20While%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20it%20has%20snatched%20power%20from%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Original%20Anti-Corruption%20Plank%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20AAP's%20parent%20organisation%2C%20India%20Against%20Corruption%2C%20was%20born%20out%20of%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20the%20UPA-II.%20Its%20politics%20was%20largely%20anti-Congress%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20a%20stance%20that%20has%20today%20shifted%20to%20opposing%20the%20BJP%20as%20it%20occupies%20the%20pole%20position%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrategists%20believe%20that%20since%20both%20parties%20have%20complementary%20vote%20blocks%2C%20the%20transfer%20of%20votes%20would%20be%20seamless.%20Optics-wise.%20the%20alliance%20is%20good%20as%20it%20comes%20after%20a%20series%20of%20setbacks%20for%20I.N.D.I.A.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectorally%2C%20however%2C%20the%20alliance%20may%20not%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20where%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20is%20very%20high%2C%20and%20in%20Haryana%2C%20where%20the%20AAP%20has%20no%20demonstrated%20support.%20In%20Delhi%20though%2C%20where%20the%20combined%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20is%20less%20than%20the%20BJP's%2C%20the%20alliance%20can%20have%20a%20decent%20impact%20if%20the%20BJP%20doesn't%20change%20its%20candidates%2C%20against%20many%20of%20whom%20anti-incumbency%20is%20brewing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20CPI(M)-Congress%20Experiment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20optics%20nonetheless%20achieve%20is%20that%20they%20help%20build%20a%20narrative%20that%20I.N.D.I.A%20is%20not%20going%20to%20give%20a%20free%20pass%20to%20the%20BJP%20without%20a%20fight.%20Being%20allies%20in%20one%20state%20and%20enemies%20in%20another%20creates%20confusion%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20tried%20a%20similar%20experiment%20in%20West%20Bengal%20with%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist).%20Main%20opponents%20in%20Kerala%2C%20the%20two%20had%20joined%20hands%20in%20West%20Bengal%20both%20in%202016%20and%202021.%20The%20elections%20of%20Kerala%20and%20Bengal%20are%20conducted%20around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20along%20with%20three%20other%20states.%20In%20both%202016%20and%202021%2C%20the%20alliance%20failed%20to%20defeat%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%202021%20it%20couldn't%20win%20even%20a%20single%20seat%2C%20and%20in%202016%2C%20its%20tally%20was%20lower%20than%20in%202011.%20The%20alliance%20was%20repeated%20in%20Tripura%20in%202023%2C%20and%20it%20again%20failed%20to%20unseat%20the%20BJP.%20The%20point%20is%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20CPI(M)%20have%20a%20long%20history%20of%20rivalry%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20when%20they%20come%2C%20together%20it%20doesn't%20cut%20much%20ice%20with%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EDays%20Of%20Pragmatic%20Politics%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20analysts%20see%20the%20latest%20developments%20as%20an%20era%20of%20pragmatic%20politics%2C%20where%20even%20staunch%20opponents%20can%20come%20together%20to%20defeat%20a%20common%20enemy%20in%20a%20particular%20election%20while%20maintaining%20a%20safe%20distance%20in%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20paint%20this%20alliance%20as%20opportunist%2C%20opportunism%20is%20perhaps%20the%20norm%20in%20Indian%20politics.%20The%20BJP's%20welcoming%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%20into%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20fold%20again%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20appointment%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20are%20all%20part%20of%20practical%20politics.%20And%20so%20is%20the%20AAP-Congress%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that's%20not%20the%20main%20issue%20here.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20such%20a%20formula%20is%20being%20tried.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20CPI(M)-Congress%20alliance's%20experience%20says%2C%20it's%20best%20not%20to%20confuse%20voters%20with%20ties%20that%20keep%20changing%20according%20to%20circumstances.%20It's%20akin%20to%20taking%20voters%20for%20a%20ride.%20Will%20the%20AAP-Congress%20alliance%20work%20in%202024%3F%20%3Cem%3EJanta%20janardhan%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709039520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvu8dmsjo_arvind-kejriwal-rahul-gandhi-rahul-kejriwal-650_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Faap-congress-alliance-is-good-optics-but-it-can-confuse-voters-5137579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20experience%20of%20CPI(M)-Congress%20alliance%20in%20the%20past%20showed%20that%20it's%20best%20not%20to%20confuse%20voters%20with%20alliances%20that%20keep%20changing%20according%20to%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20time.%20It's%20akin%20to%20taking%20voters%20for%20a%20ride.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Faap-congress-alliance-is-good-optics-but-it-can-confuse-voters-5137579%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Faap-congress-alliance-is-good-optics-but-it-can-confuse-voters-5137579%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Faap-congress-alliance-is-good-optics-but-it-can-confuse-voters-5137579%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Kahar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27183834%2FPalanquin-Kahar-Pic-credit-NYPL1-e1709039448261.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Kahar%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E(2%2C155%2C644%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20caste%20group%20we%20are%20going%20to%20discuss%20today%20is%20Kahar.%20They%20are%20also%20known%20as%20Ramani%2C%20Rawani%20and%20Kamkar.%20Now%2C%20some%20people%20have%20also%20started%20referring%20to%20them%20as%20Chandravanshi.%20There%20are%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20among%20Kahars.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20things%20changed%20as%20human%20civilization%20progressed.%20Thought%20processes%20changed%20and%20even%20the%20connotations%20of%20words.%20But%20some%20things%20have%20remained%20intact%20like%20the%20strong%20shoulders%20of%20palanquin%20bearers%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekahars%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Carrying%20Brahmins%2C%20priests%2C%20kings%2C%20and%20other%20landlords%20in%20palanquins%20and%20ferrying%20them%20to%20their%20destinations%20was%20their%20job.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20261px)%2085vw%2C%20261px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22261%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22374%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20K%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eahars%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20did%20not%20even%20have%20slippers%20on%20their%20feet.%20When%20they%20moved%20with%20the%20heavy%20load%20on%20their%20shoulders%2C%20they%20used%20to%20make%20a%20unique%20sound%20to%20boost%20their%20spirits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20one%20finds%20mention%20of%20slavery%20in%20the%20history%20of%20western%20countries%2C%20the%20concept%20has%20been%20concealed%20behind%20the%20veil%20of%20caste%20in%20Indian%20history.%20Kahar%20and%20Kamkar%20were%20caste%20groups%20whose%20members%20were%20forced%20to%20bear%20the%20burden%20of%20others.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20Kahars%2C%20or%20Chandravanshis%20of%20the%20feudal%20system%2C%20primarily%20reside%20in%20Bengal%2C%20Bihar%20and%20the%20eastern%20areas%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20addition%20to%20other%20states.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20any%20rights%20on%20agricultural%20land%20or%20farming%2C%20nor%20do%20they%20have%20many%20rights%20now.%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20only%20sought%20after%20when%20someone%20is%20getting%20married.%20They%20used%20to%20work%20as%20a%20group%20and%20chose%20the%20palanquin%20or%20the%20group%20as%20per%20their%20status.%20Generally%2C%20they%20worked%20in%20groups%20of%20four%20%E2%80%93%20two%20each%20at%20the%20front%20and%20the%20back%20%E2%80%93%20while%20the%20person%20sitting%20in%20the%20palanquin%20at%20the%20centre%20travelled%20comfortably.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20their%20sincerity%20in%20the%20job%2C%20the%20members%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20have%20been%20oppressed%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20feudal%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20times%20have%20changed%20and%20science%20and%20technology%20have%20advanced.%20Roads%20have%20been%20built.%20Uneven%20and%20narrow%20walkways%20are%20gone%20and%20vehicles%20have%20become%20available.%20Yet%20even%20now%2C%20affluent%20people%20seek%20their%20services%20while%20planning%20a%20wedding.%20The%20number%20of%20palanquin-bearers%20has%20reduced%20significantly%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20crisis%20of%20livelihood%20is%20looming%20over%20the%20community.%20They%20already%20had%20a%20dearth%20of%20land%20and%20whatever%20little%20bit%20of%20land%20there%20was%2C%20has%20been%20divided%20further.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20say%20how%20much%20immovable%20property%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20present%20generation%20of%20this%20caste%20group.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20documents%20of%20Bihar%20government%2C%20their%20total%20population%20is%202%2C155%2C644%20and%20they%20are%20included%20in%20the%20extremely%20backward%20class.%20Though%20they%20are%20not%20considered%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%2C%20their%20condition%20is%20no%20better%20than%20that%20of%20Dalit%20communities%E2%80%99.%20For%20example%2C%20only%201.5%25%20to%202%25%20of%20their%20population%20participates%20in%20government%20jobs%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20caste%20group%20is%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20political%20Hinduisation%20now.%20To%20alienate%20them%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%2C%20they%20are%20being%20told%20that%20they%20are%20not%20Kahar%20but%20Chandravanshi.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20is%20claimed%20that%20the%20Chandravansh%2C%20or%20lunar%20dynasty%2C%20was%20a%20Kshatriya%20caste%20of%20ancient%20India.%20Sometimes%2C%20to%20pit%20them%20against%20the%20Yadavas%2C%20it%20is%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Krishna%20was%20born%20in%20the%20Yaduvansh%20branch%20of%20the%20Chandravansh.%20They%20even%20call%20Kahar%20caste%20members%20descendants%20of%20Jarasandha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChange%20is%20necessary%20because%20other%20OBC%20caste%20groups%20often%20do%20not%20mingle%20with%20them%20while%20Dalits%20do%20not%20consider%20them%20one%20of%20their%20own.%20One%20needs%20to%20understand%20the%20social%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20dilemma%20of%20this%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F263539%2Fbihar-caste-survey-kahaar-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-su