Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fsandeshkhali-unrest-as-women-led-protests-escalate-tmcs-outsider-claims-find-little-resonance%5C%22%3ESandeshkhali%20Unrest%3A%20As%20Women-Led%20Protests%20Escalate%2C%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Outsider%E2%80%99%20Claims%20Find%20Little%20Resonance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20made%20controversial%20statements%20regarding%20sexual%20assault%20cases.%20They%20rather%20follow%20a%20pattern%20often%20set%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPast%20instances%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fnadia-rape-victim-family-fear-hanskhali-mamata-love-affair-comment-1936993-2022-04-13%5C%22%3ETrinamool%20supremo%20had%20raised%20doubts%20about%20the%20gangrape-murder%20of%20a%2014-year-old%20girl%20in%20Nadia%20district%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20victim%2C%20invited%20to%20a%20birthday%20party%20by%20the%20son%20of%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20in%20Hanshkhali%20was%20allegedly%20gang-raped%20by%20the%20youth%20and%20his%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20died%20due%20to%20excessive%20bleeding%2C%20and%20family%20members%20were%20reportedly%20prevented%20from%20seeking%20medical%20help.%20Following%20her%20death%20local%20Trinamool%20workers%20attacked%20the%20family%2C%20pointing%20a%20gun%20and%20forcefully%20cremated%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20later%20used%20the%20child%20helpline%20to%20raise%20the%20complaint.%20Banerjee%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20then%20West%20Bengal%20police%20chief%20Manoj%20Malaviya%2C%20suggested%20the%20girl%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20the%20accused%2C%20leading%20to%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20opposition%20parties.%20The%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20subsequently%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2F