ed%20the%20Park%20Street%20rape%20case%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Esajano%20golpo%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fabricated%20story)%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20was%20orchestrated%20by%20the%20media%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20the%20police%20and%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20even%20suggested%20that%20the%20victim%2C%20Suzette%20Jordan%2C%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Csex%20worker%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20rape%20resulted%20from%20a%20dispute%20with%20a%20client.%20The%20police%20investigation%2C%20led%20by%20IPS%20Damayanti%20Sen%2C%20revealed%20that%20the%20woman%20had%20been%20raped%20by%20a%20gang%20of%20four%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20was%20soon%20shifted%20from%20her%20post%20as%20joint%20commissioner%20of%20Kolkata%20Police%20(Crime)%20to%20the%20insignificant%20post%20of%20DIG%20(Training)%20at%20Barrackpore%20Police%20Training%20College%20and%20then%20again%20to%20DIG%2C%20(Darjeeling%20Range)%2C%20within%20four%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20ordered%20Sen%20to%20supervise%20four%20rape%20incidents%20in%20Matia%2C%20Ingrejbazar%2C%20Deganga%20and%20Banshdroni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20weeks%20later%2C%20Banerjee%20labelled%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Frape-allegation-planned-by-cpim-mamata%2Farticle2942200.ece%5C%22%3Ealleged%20rape%20case%20on%20a%20train%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconspiracy%20by%20the%20CPI(M)%E2%80%9D%20to%20tarnish%20her%20government%E2%80%99s%20reputation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20identified%20the%20victim%20as%20the%20wife%20of%20a%20CPI(M)%20worker%2C%20despite%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20five%20accused%20were%20eventually%20found%20guilty%20of%20armed%20robbery%20but%20not%20guilty%20in%20the%20gang%20rape%20case.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2