2%80%99s%20striking%20down%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Scheme%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20%E2%80%9Canother%20opportunity%20to%20refine%20the%20system%E2%80%9D%20of%20political%20funding%20and%20not%20merely%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvictory%20or%20defeat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20incisive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fsc-electoral-bonds-judgment-9175075%2F%5C%22%3Epiece%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Lavasa%20asks%20probing%20questions%20regarding%20the%20way%20forward%20for%20political%20funding%20and%20democracy%20in%20India%20now%20that%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Scheme%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWill%20this%20judgment%20lead%20us%20back%20to%20the%20dark%20alleys%20of%20cash%20funding%3F%20That%20is%20a%20legitimate%20concern.%20The%20government%20must%20consult%20all%20stakeholders%20in%20coming%20up%20with%20another%20alternative%20with%20strong%20sunshine%20clauses%20to%20address%20the%20rot%20that%20political%20funding%20has%20fallen%20into%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20offers%2C%20as%20a%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asks%20pointedly%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20funds%20raised%20under%20the%20scheme%20which%20the%20top%20court%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CFinally%2C%20will%20this%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20case%20of%20closing%20the%20stables%20after%20the%20horses%20have%20bolted%3F%20What%20would%20be%20the%20nature%20and%20fate%20of%20funds%20raised%20under%20an%20%E2%80%98unconstitutional%E2%80%99%20scheme%3F%20Is%20the%20violator%20entitled%20to%20enjoy%20the%20fruits%20of%20the%20violation%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CMarch%2013%20is%20expected%20to%20lift%20the%20veil%20but%20will%20those%20blinded%20by%20the%20blaze%20of%20self-discovered%20glory%20see%20anything%20pernicious%3F%20Let%20not%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20impending%20elections%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20the%20SC%20judgement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20elections%20around%20the%20corner%20and%20a%20new%20Lok%20Sabha%20set%20to%20be%20constituted%20soon%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20hope%20the%20new%20parliament%20will%20bring%20about%20a%20law%20showing%20full%20respect%20to%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20SC%20so%20that%20India%20can%20justifiably%20hail%20itself%20as%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy%20without%20being%20accused%20of%20giving%20democracy%20a%20stepmotherly%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hoping%20for%20more%20transparency%20going%20forward%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20political%20parties%20operate%2C%20he%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20hope%20there%20are%20no%20sudden%20clouds%20that%20thwart%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%20strike%E2%80%A6%20The%20SC%20deserves%20to%20be%20complimented%20for%20the%20clarity%20of%20its%20arguments%20and%20courage%20in%20pronouncing%20the%20issues%20convincingly%2C%20rather%20than%20providing%20a%20robe%20of%20legitimacy%20to%20naked%20unconstitutionality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20election%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20at%20the%20Election%20Commission%20was%20cut%20short%20allegedly%20for%20his%20rulings%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20He%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-elections-lavasa-opposed-five-clean-chits-to-amit-shah-pm-modi-5710773%2F%5C%22%3Eopposed%20five%20clean%20chits%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0given%20by%20the%20poll%20body%20to%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20over%20alleged%20violations%20of%20the%20poll%20code.%20The%20Modi%20government%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-commissioner-ashok-lavasa-known-for-dissent-in-ec-may-leave-early-for-adb-job%5C%22%3Eremoved%3C%