0not%20immediately%20noticed%20in%20a%20heavily%20surveilled%20area%20such%20as%20this%2C%20adding%20that%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20lane%20had%20been%20cordoned%20off%20for%20a%20function%20and%20was%20full%20of%20catering%20staff%20and%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20media%20reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Fdelhi-ncr%2Ftwo-year-old-mauled-to-death-as-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-her-drag-her-several-meters-46058%5C%22%3Eciting%20eyewitness%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20also%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20as%2C%20according%20to%20the%20note%2C%20the%20police%20found%20no%20eyewitnesses%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20police%20officer%20to%20reach%20the%20hospital%20said%20that%20he%20found%20no%20eye-witnesses%20to%20the%20incident%20amongst%20the%20family.%20He%20has%20further%20recorded%20that%20upon%20returning%20to%20the%20site%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20he%20found%20no%20eye-witnesses%20amongst%20the%20crowd%20of%20residents%2C%20onlookers%2C%20visitors%20and%20others%20who%20were%20present%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnhrc.nic.in%2Fmedia%2Fpress-release%2Fnhrc-takes-suo-motu-cognizance-stray-dog-mauling-2-year-old-girl-new-delhi%5C%22%3ENational%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2027)%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20reports%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20incident%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20an%20isolated%20case%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20had%20previously%20directed%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20civic%20authorities%20to%20control%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20stray%20dog%20population%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20relevant%20Union%20government%20rules%20following%20%E2%80%9Cearlier%20tragic%20incidents%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20it%20had%20issued%20notices%20to%20officials%20in%20Delhi%20seeking%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20the%20incident%20within%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20government%20%E2%80%9Cis%20expected%20to%20inform%20whether%20any%20relief%20has%20been%20given%20to%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20next%20of%20kin%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20NHRC%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilar%20incidents%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20and%20as%20such%20this%20is%20not%20a%20problem%20for%20any%20one%20state%20or%20Union%20territory.%20The%20situation%20is%20grim%20and%20alarming%2C%20requiring%20immediate%20and%20effective%20action%20by%20the%20authorities%20without%20any%20delay%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20activists%2C%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20family%20housed%20an%20unfriendly%20dog%20(a%20type%20of%20pit%20bull)%20that%20they%20used%20for%20breeding%20purposes.%20Questions%20have%20been%20raised%20around%20the%20pit%20bull%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20incident%20and%20if%20the%20child%20was%20left%20unattended%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20activists%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20unchecked%2C%20illegal%20breeding%20of%20dogs%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20conditions%20in%20which%20these%20animals%20are%20kept%20that%20leads%20to%20them%20being%20hostile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20request%20the%20authorities%20to%20examine%20all%20the%20surrounding%20CCTV%20footage%20before%20reaching%20any%20conclusion%20about%20this%20child%E2%80%99s%20death.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20evidence%2C%20footage%2C%20eye-%20witnesses%20or%20even%20a%20post-mortem%20report%2C%20every%20media%20story%20has%20unequivocally%20blamed%20the%20tragedy%20on%20the%20community%20dogs.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20this%20hate-mongering%2C%20two%20dogs%20of%20the%20area%20have%20already%20been%20bludgeoned%20to%20death%20in%20cold%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20activists%20said%20that%20since%20it%20is%20a%20high%20security%20area%2C%20it%20is%20reasonable%20to%20expect%20that%20irrefutable%20evidence%20can%20be%20found%20to%20determine%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20child%20instead%20of%20blaming%20it%20on%20stray%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20was%20signed%20by%20Anjali%20Gopalan%2C%20managing%20trustee%2C%20All%20Creatures%20Great%20and%20Small%20and%20executive%20director%2C%20The%20Naz%20Foundation%20(India)%2C%20Geeta%20Seshamani%2C%20vice-president%2C%20Friendicoes%20and%20co-founder%2C%20Wildlife%20SOS%2C%20Ambika%20Shukla%2C%20trustee%2C%20People%20for%20Animals%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Percival%20Billimoria%2C%20Shernaz%20Italia%20and%20Freny%20Kodaiji%2C%20trustees%2C%20DogMatters%20as%20well%20as%20Tilak%20Nanda%20and%20Kavita%20Rai%20who%20are%20residents%20of%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709035952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2F6801981960_5f6b0d02ab_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanimal-activists-question-stray-dog-theory-in-tughlaq-lane-mauling-incident%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20activists%20said%20that%20since%20it%20is%20a%20high%20security%20area%2C%20it%20is%20reasonable%20to%20expect%20that%20irrefutable%20evidence%20can%20be%20found%20to%20determine%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20child%20instead%20of%20blaming%20it%20on%20stray%20dogs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanimal-activists-question-stray-dog-theory-in-tughlaq-lane-mauling-incident%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Has%20%26quot%3BLost%20Majority%26quot%3B%20In%20Himachal%2C%20Claims%20BJP's%20Jairam%20Thakur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Jairam%20Thakur%20on%20Tuesday%20claimed%20that%20the%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu-led%20Congress%20government%20is%20in%20a%20minority%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20the%20State%20BJP%20would%20demand%20a%20floor%20test%2C%20Mr%20Thakur%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20budget%20will%20be%20presented%20tomorrow.%20We%20will%20discuss%20the%20budget%20tomorrow%20and%20then%20we%20will%20see%20the%20situation%20there.%20But%20I%20can%20see%20that%20the%20government%20has%20lost%20the%20majority.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20is%20underway%20for%20a%20high-octane%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20battle%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20exuded%20hope%20in%20its%20candidate%20winning%20the%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E67%20out%20of%20the%20total%2068%20legislators%20have%20exercised%20their%20votes%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Shimla%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20Sudarshan%20Singh%20Babloo%2C%20Congress%20MLA%2C%20has%20not%20come%20so%20far%20due%20to%20illness.%20He%20was%20hospitalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20fierce%20competition%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20for%20the%20sole%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20between%20Congress%20candidate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20and%20the%20BJP's%20Harsh%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20Mahajan%20is%20a%20three-time%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20former%20minister%20who%20resigned%20from%20the%20party%20in%20September%202022%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20a%20clear%20majority%20with%2040%20out%20of%2068%20MLAs%20and%20the%20support%20of%20three%20independent%20MLAs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%2025%20MLAs%2C%20is%20far%20behind%20in%20the%20number%20game%2C%20it%20has%20forced%20a%20contest%20by%20fielding%20Mahajan%20against%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Congress%20issued%20a%20whip%20to%20its%20MLAs%20to%20vote%20for%20party%20candidate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20whip%2C%20all%20the%20candidates%20will%20have%20to%20show%20the%20ballot%20to%20the%20authorised%20agent%2C%20who%20can%20declare%20a%20vote%20invalid%20if%20any%20MLA%20refuses%20to%20show%20the%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20BJP%20nominee%20complained%20to%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20issued%20a%20three-line%20whip%20to%20its%20MLAs%20for%20the%20polls%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20unethical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20a%20whip%20is%20not%20only%20unethical%20but%20also%20against%20the%20conducting%20of%20elections%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20as%20it%20will%20affect%20the%20decision-making%20ability%20of%20the%20MLAs%2C%26quot%3B%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20said%20in%20his%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20complaint%20was%20filed%2C%20the%20Congress%20hit%20out%20at%20BJP%20State%20Minister%20Harsh%20Wardhan%20Chauhan%2C%20who%20said%20that%20the%20charges%20to%20the%20poll%20body%20were%20a%20result%20of%20'frustration'%20in%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20Wardhan%20Chauhan%2C%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Minister%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20planning%20%26quot%3Bhorse%20trading%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20BJP's%20frustration%20because%20the%20number%20of%20MLAs%20is%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP.%2040%20MLAs%20are%20with%20Congress%2C%20and%203%20are%20independent.%20The%20BJP%20only%20has%2025%20MLAs.%20...even%20without%20numbers%2C%20BJP%20is%20fielding%20their%20candidate%2C%20which%20means%20they're%20planning%20horse%20trading...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chauhan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20for%2056%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20from%2015%20states%2C%20which%20are%20falling%20vacant%20in%20April%2C%20is%20being%20held%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20for%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20is%20six%20years%2C%20and%20elections%20are%20held%20after%20every%20two%20years%20for%2033%20per%20c