als%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98MEMU%2FDEMU%20Express%E2%80%99%20Trains%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Frailways-restore-passenger-train-fares%2Farticle67890663.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20lockdown%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20Railways%20had%20been%20criticised%20for%20their%20gradual%20withdrawal%20of%20%E2%80%98Passenger%20Trains%E2%80%99%20by%20simply%20changing%20their%20names.%20%E2%80%98Ordinary%20Class%E2%80%99%20fares%20were%20done%20away%20with%20and%20the%20minimum%20cost%20of%20ticket%20went%20up%20from%20Rs%2010%20to%20a%20whopping%20three-fold%2C%20to%20Rs%2030.%20This%20was%20at%20par%20with%20Express%20Train%20fares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20railway%20sources%2C%20writes%20the%20newspaper%2C%20the%20Chief%20Booking%20Reservation%20Supervisors%20were%20informed%20that%20the%20minimum%20fare%20in%20Second%20Class%20Ordinary%20Trains%20had%20been%20reversed%20with%20effect%20from%20the%20early%20hours.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20this%20followed%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Railway%20Board%20on%20February%2026%20to%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20slashing%20of%20fares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Railways%20had%20come%20under%20criticism%20for%20charging%20commuters%2C%20%E2%80%9Cespecially%20small%20vendors%2C%20daily%20wage%20workers%20and%20other%20poor%20passengers%2C%20are%20paying%20double%20the%20charge%20for%20travelling%20in%20the%20same%20slow-moving%20train.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20recorded%20how%20the%20change%20in%20name%2C%20without%20a%20change%20in%20speed%20had%20resulted%20in%20higher%20prices%20paid%20by%20those%20who%20could%20least%20afford%20to.%20The%20move%20will%20bolster%20the%20Railways%20financially%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fexplainers%2Fhas-indian-railways-replaced-passenger-trains-with-express-specials-what-will-be-the-fare-structure-8793114.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20a%20news%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20yesterday%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20it%20will%20be%20a%20huge%20burden%20to%20the%20economically%20disadvantaged%20commuters%20such%20as%20small%20vendors%2C%20daily%20wage%20labourers%2C%20farmers%20who%20depend%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Caffordable%E2%80%9D%20fares%20of%20the%20trains%20for%20transportation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20Indian%20railways%20as%20a%20public%20good%2C%20to%20enable%20the%20least%20advantaged%20in%20a%20large%20country%20was%20questioned%20by%20others.%20Former%20railway%20officer%2C%20Mathew%20John%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-indian-railways-hype-and-reality%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20%E2%80%9Chas%20historically%20been%20the%20mode%20of%20transport%20for%20the%C2%A0common%20people%2C%20who%20have%20hitherto%20been%20the%20Railway%20management%E2%80%99s%20prime%20focus.%E2%80%9D%20The%20%E2%80%9Cvision%20statement%E2%80%9D%20of%202011-12%20he%20noted%2C%20has%20stated%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20Railways%20shall%20provide%20safe%2C%20efficient%2C%20AFFORDABLE%2C%20customer-focussed%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20transport%2C%20clearly%20spelling%20out%20its%20concern%20for%20the%20common%20person%20i.e.%2C%20the%20second-class%20traveller.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20wrote%20that%20there%20were%20questionable%20practices%20adopted%20to%20give%20the%20appearance%20of%20boosted%20performance%2C%20like%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20average%20freight%20train%20speeds%20which%20were%2027.2%20kmph%20in%202010-11%20declined%20to%2024.4%20kmph%20in%202019-20%20but%20then%2C%20quite%20inexplicably%2C%20shot%20up%20to%2043.2%20kmph%20in%202020-21%20and%2037.3%20kmph%20in%202021-22%20by%20employing%20the%20simple%20artifice%20of%20deducting%20the%20period%20of%20major%20detentions%20enroute.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegarding%20financial%20performance%2C%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20has%20pointed%20out%20the%20fudging%20of%20the%20operating%20ratio%20by%20removing%20pension%20expenditure%20appropriated%20to%20the%20pension%20fund%20from%20the%20computation%20of%20profitability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709035252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27163018%2F21323848_8c73135d33_e.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpassenger-trains-express-railway-fares%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Railways%20were%20criticised%20as%20%E2%80%98Ordinary%20Class%E2%80%99%20fares%20were%20done%20away%20with%20and%20the%20minimum%20cost%20of%20ticket%20went%20up%20from%20Rs%2010%20to%20a%20whopping%20three-fold%2C%20to%20Rs%2030.%20This%20was%20at%20par%20with%20Express%20Train%20fares.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpassenger-trains-express-railway-fares%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAre%20You%20Ready%3F%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20Asks%20India%20Star%20Who%20Said%20He's%20Been%20%26quot%3BHumiliated%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20star%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hanuma%20Vihari%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1684-hanuma-vihari-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHanuma%20Vihari%3C%2Fa%3E%20brought%20forward%20some%20serious%20allegations%20against%20one%20of%20his%20teammates%20in%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20team%2C%20saying%20he%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bhumiliated%26quot%3B%