ring%20that%20game%20I%20shouted%20at%20the%2017th%20player%20and%20he%20complained%20to%20his%20dad%20(who%20is%20a%20politician)%2C%20his%20dad%20in%20return%20asked%20the%20association%20to%20take%20action%20against%20me.%20Although%20we%20chased%20410%20against%20last%20year's%20finalists%20Bengal%2C%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20resign%20from%20captaincy%20without%20any%20fault%20of%20mine.%20I%20never%20said%20anything%20on%20a%20personal%20note%20to%20the%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vihari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20player%20in%20question%2C%20KN%20Prudhvi%20Raj%2C%20took%20to%20Instagram%20and%20accused%20Vihari%20of%20making%20false%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHello%20everyone!%20I'm%20that%20guy%2C%20you%20guys%20are%20searching%20in%20the%20comment%20box%2C%20whatever%20you%20guys%20heard%20is%20absolutely%20false%2C%20no%20one%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20game%20and%20my%20self-respect%20is%20much%20bigger%20than%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPersonal%20attacks%20and%20vulgar%20language%20are%20unacceptable%20in%20any%20kind%20of%20human%20platform.%20Everyone%20in%20the%20team%20knows%20what%20happened%20that%20day.%20Nuvu%20inthaku%20minchi%20emmi%20pikkulevu%20(You%20can't%20get%20any%20better%20than%20this)%20Mr%20so%20called%20champion.%20Play%20this%20sympathy%20game%20however%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Prudhvi%20Raj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Vihari%20later%20shared%20the%20copy%20of%20his%20statement%20on%20his%20X%20account%20which%20was%20signed%20by%20other%20players%20in%20the%20Andhra%20team%20with%20a%20one-line%20comment%20--%20%26quot%3Bthe%20whole%20team%20knows.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20the%2030-year-old%20expressed%20grouse%20that%20the%20association%20did%20not%20value%20his%20sacrifices%20for%20the%20team%20over%20the%20years%2C%20recalling%20last%20year's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarterfinal%20match%20against%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20forearm%20injury%20to%20his%20right-hand%20had%20forced%20him%20to%20bat%20left-handed%20in%20that%20game%2C%20but%20he%20could%20not%20prevent%20Andhra's%20ouster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20association%20thought%20that%20player%20was%20more%20important%20than%20the%20guy%20who%20gave%20his%20body%20on%20the%20line%20last%20year%20and%20batted%20left-handed%2C%20took%20Andhra%20to%20knock%20outs%205%20times%20in%20the%20last%207%20years%20and%20played%20for%20India%20in%2016%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20embarrassed%20but%20the%20only%20reason%20I%20continued%20playing%20this%20season%20was%20because%20I%20respect%20the%20game%20and%20my%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20there%20was%20an%20interaction%20between%20Indian%20cricket%20tam%20star%20bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Hanuma%20Vihari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20asked%20Vihari%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BKutty%20stories%20with%20ash%20%26quot%3B%20Vihari%20Garu%20%26quot%3B%20Meeru%20ready%20unnara%20(Are%20you%20ready)%3F%3F%3F%3F%C2%A0%20%40Hanumavihari%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20which%20Hanuma%20Vihari%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BMeru%20Epudu%20ante%20apudu%20(When%20you%20mean%20then)%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22lv%5C%22%3EMeru%20Epudu%20ante%20apudu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAQFP44g4ta%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAQFP44g4ta%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Hanuma%20vihari%20(%40Hanumavihari)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHanumavihari%2Fstatus%2F1762111522505896109%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2026%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20bitter%20spat%20b