ted%20after%20all%20House%20members%20are%20notified.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fno-assembly-session-can-be-called-without-notifying-reserved-seats-says-imran-khans-party%2Farticleshow%2F108039612.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fno-assembly-session-can-be-called-without-notifying-reserved-seats-says-imran-khans-party%2Famp_articleshow%2F108039612.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fno-assembly-session-can-be-called-without-notifying-reserved-seats-says-imran-khans-party%2Famp_articleshow%2F108039612.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Keeping%20the%20Global%20Struggle%20Alive%20for%20Freeing%20Up%20the%20Commons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27142248%2FUntitled-design-17.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20understanding%20of%20the%20relation%20between%20science%2C%20technology%20and%20the%20socio-economic%20and%20historical%20conditions%20through%20which%20they%20evolve%20is%20known%20to%20be%20central%20to%20the%20analysis%20of%20the%20drivers%20of%20social%20change%20and%20transformation.%20As%20a%20trained%20and%20practicing%20%3Cem%3Etechnologist%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20a%20scholarly%20interest%20in%20science%20and%20its%20history%2C%20and%20as%20a%20social%20and%20political%20activist%20committed%20to%20struggles%20for%20establishing%20an%20egalitarian%20and%20just%20society%2C%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20has%2C%20over%20a%20long%20career%2C%20engaged%20with%20those%20issues.%20The%20book%20under%20review%20is%20a%20revised%20and%20updated%20collection%20of%20the%20wide-ranging%20contributions%20he%20has%20made%20as%20an%20analyst%20and%20public%20intellectual%20in%20the%20course%20of%20that%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20understated%20manner%2C%20Purkayastha%20differentiates%20his%20approach%20and%20stance%20to%20the%20multiple%20issues%20discussed%20in%20this%20book%2C%20from%20that%20adopted%20by%20most%20progressive%20and%20not-so-progressive%20writers%20on%20the%20subject.%20In%20the%20introduction%2C%20he%20notes%20that%20unlike%20scientists%2C%20who%20in%20the%20past%20came%20from%20a%20university%20background%20in%20which%20they%20were%20also%20taught%20philosophy%2C%20engineers%20came%20from%20%E2%80%98trade%20schools%E2%80%99%20in%20which%20they%20were%20taught%20to%20dirty%20their%20hands%20to%20build%20the%20artefacts%20that%20powered%20investment%20and%20facilitated%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20316px)%2085vw%2C%20316px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27142402%2Fprabir_p_knowledge_as_commons_cover_front.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27142402%2Fprabir_p_knowledge_as_commons_cover_front.jpg%20786w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27142402%2Fprabir_p_knowledge_as_commons_cover_front-197x300.jpg%20197w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27142402%2Fprabir_p_knowledge_as_commons_cover_front-671x1024.jpg%20671w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699096%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22482%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKnowledge%20as%20Commons%3A%20Towards%20Inclusive%20Science%20and%20Technology%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Prabir%20Purkayastha.%20Publisher%3A%20Leftword%20Books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20objective%20of%20science%20is%20to%20know%20nature%E2%80%9D%2C%20whereas%20that%20of%20technology%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbuilding%20an%20artefact%3B%20in%20other%20words%2C%20of%20changing%20nature%E2%80%9D.%20Hence%20technologists%20were%20not%20too%20concerned%20with%20the%20philosophical%20basis%20of%20and%20the%20existential%20nature%20of%20their%20work%20and%20output.%20This%20has%20meant%20that%2C%20throughout%20history%2C%20science%20was%20privileged%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20world%20of%20ideas%20and%20knowledge%2C%20whereas%20technology%20was%20seen%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20world%20of%20work%20that%20delivered%20artefacts%20in%20activity%20pursued%20either%20as%20%E2%80%98craft%E2%80%99%20or%20based%20on%20using%20scientific%20knowledge.%20In%20the%20event%2C%20as%20Purkayastha%20found%2C%20discussions%20on%20science%2C%20technology%20and%20society%20were%20substantially%20denuded%20of%20the%20insights%20that%20came%20from%20the%20viewpoint%20of%20the%20technologist%2C%20which%20made%20him%20conscious%20of%20the%20need%20to%20abjure%20the%20tendency%20to%20treat%20%E2%80%9Ctechnology%20as%20a%20sideshow%20of%20science.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technologist%E2%80%99s%20objective%20of%20using%20science%20to%20build%20artefacts%20that%20perform%20pre-specified%20tasks%20and%20deliver%20premeditated%20results%20very%20often%20entailed%20a%20need%20to%20go%20beyond%20science%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbridge%20the%20gap%20between%20what%20is%20known%20and%20what%20is%20not%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20process%20there%20is%20need%20to%20rework%20the%20scientific%20understanding%20of%20the%20fundamental%20relationships%20of%20nature%2C%20with%20implications%20for%20science.%20Science%20sets%20the%20envelope%20defining%20what%20technology%20cannot%20do%2C%20while%20technology%20opens%20up%20new%20opportunities%20for%20scientific%20advance.%20This%20interdependence%20and%20even%20interpenetration%20of%20science%20and%20technology%20are%20investigated%20in%20more%20than%20one%20essay%20in%20the%20book%2C%20with%20forays%20into%20philosophy%2C%20discussions%20of%20the%20special%20characteristics%20of%20the%20two%20forms%20of%20knowledge%2C%20and%20illustrations%20from%20the%20history%20of%20science%20and%20technology.%20What%20emerges%20and%20is%20emphasised%20is%20that%20both%20these%20branches%20of%20knowledge%20are%20the%20common%20heritage%20of%20humankind%2C%20and%20must%20belong%20in%20the%20final%20analysis%20to%20all%20of%20society%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20global%20commons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20however%2C%20has%20historically%20not%20been%20the%20case.%20Decisions%20on%20what%20directions%20the%20pursuit%20of%20scientific%20knowledge%20must%20take%2C%20on%20how%20available%20knowledge%20to%20produce%20new%20artefacts%20must%20be%20deployed%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20artefacts%20that%20need%20to%20be%20produced%20and%20the%20resultant%20use%20to%20which%20science%20and%20technology%20are%20put%20are%20embedded%20in%20specific%20social%20and%20historical%20contexts.%20Besides%20exploring%20the%20nature%20of%20science%20and%20technology%20and%20their%20relationship%2C%20the%20essays%20in%20the%20volume%20examine%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20influence%20that%20the%20socio-economic%20contexts%20in%20which%20science%20and%20technology%20evolve%20or%20are%20sought%20to%20be%20developed%20and%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdhering%20to%20the%20Marxist%20view%20that%20scientific%20laws%20reflect%20an%20objective%20material%20reality%2C%20the%20author%20is%20quick%20to%20note%20that%20Marxists%20also%20hold%20that%20scientific%20knowledge%20emerges%20and%20advances%20in%20response%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20society%20at%20different%20points%20of%20time%20in%20history.%20Social%20factors%20and%20discrimination%20linked%20to%20gender%2C%20race%20and%20caste%20that%20influence%20social%20development%20also%20affect%20scientific%20and%20technological%20practice.%20But%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Lysenko%20case%20in%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20Purkayastha%20cautions%20against%20trying%20to%20direct%20science%20based%20solely%20on%20judgements%20about%20forms%20of%20science%20being%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%E2%80%98bourgeois%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98proletarian%E2%80%99.%20While%20an%20outside%20influence%20driving%20science%20may%20be%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20ruling%20class%2C%20real%20needs%20or%20social%20concerns%20have%20also%20influenced%20scientific%20activity.%20Moreover%2C%20while%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20categories%20of%20thought%20that%20we%20use%20to%20capture%20scientific%20phenomena%20do%20owe%20their%20origin%20to%20the%20human%20being%E2%80%99s%20social%20consciousness%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%A6%20%E2%80%9Cconceptual%20categories%E2%80%94whether%20mass%2C%20momentum%2C%20or%20energy%E2%80%94may%20have%20little%20to%20do%20with%20ideology%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20indeed%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20ruling%20class%20influences%20scientific%20development.%20To%20start%20with%2C%20through%20selective%20funding%20and%20patronage%20it%20influences%20the%20choice%20of%20scientific%20problems%20addressed.%20Socially%20needed%20technologies%20that%20are%20not%20profitable%20may%20be%20starved%20of%20funding%20or%20ignored.%20Second%2C%20the%20choice%20is%20often%20determined%20by%20the%20need%20to%20reproduce%20and%20intensify%20the%20domination%20of%20capital.%C2%A0%20GM%20seeds%20developed%20by%20Monsanto%20have%20the%20benefit%20of%20ramping%20up%20corporate%20profits%20by%20eroding%20the%20ability%20of%20farmers%20to%20save%20seeds%20as%20well%20as%20by%20making%20them%20dependent%20on%20a%20range%20of%20commercial%20pesticides%20to%20ward%20off%20new%20diseases.%20Finally%2C%20in%20pursuit%20of%20profit%2C%20capital%20may%20restrict%20access%20to%20technology%2C%20even%20when%20the%20scientific%20endeavour%20underlying%20the%20development%20of%20that%20technology%20is%20substantially%20or%20almost%20wholly%20funded%20by%20the%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ways%20in%20which%20this%20occurs%20and%20the%20consequences%20are%20covered%20in%20essays%20whose%20concern%E2%80%94the%20private%20capture%20and%20enclosure%20of%20the%20knowledge%20commons%E2%80%94provide%20the%20title%20for%20the%20volume%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20signifying%20the%20importance%20of%20that%20concern%20in%20the%20perspective%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20precursors%20of%20the%20capture%20are%20the%20undertaking%20of%20science%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98planned%E2%80%99%20basis%20at%20an%20industrial%20scale%2C%20the%20integration%20of%20scientific%20and%20technological%20activity%2C%20the%20quick%20conversion%20of%20scientific%20knowledge%20into%20marketable%20applications%2C%20and%20the%20privatisation%20of%20the%20knowledge%20generated%20through%20institutional%20research%20in%20universities%20and%20laboratories.%20Even%20when%20much%20of%20the%20basic%20and%20applied%20research%20is%20funded%20by%20the%20state%2C%20capital%20intervenes%20at%20appropriate%20points%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20knowledge%20so%20generated%2C%20and%20gain%20monopoly%20%E2%80%9Cownership%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20and%20rights%20through%20the%20use%20of%20the%20international%20property%20regime%20created%20and%20strengthened%20to%20aid%20profiteering%20and%20capital%20accumulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20knowledge%20commons%20is%20enclosed%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20capital%2C%20with%20legal%20instruments%20such%20as%20the%20Bayh-Dole%20(Patent%20and%20Trademark%20Law%20Amendments)%20Act%20and%20global%20agreements%20such%20as%20that%20on%20Trade%20Related%20Intellectual%20Property%20Rights%20under%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%20facilitating%20the%20capture.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20the%20infinite%20knowledge%20commons%20in%20which%20knowledge%20does%20not%20deplete%20when%20shared%2C%20reproduced%20and%20consumed%2C%20as%20tends%20to%20happen%20with%20physical%20commons%20such%20as%20grazing%20land%2C%20is%20%E2%80%98enclosed%20to%20exclude%20some%20to%20protect%20the%20%E2%80%9Crights%E2%80%9D%20and%20profits%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20little%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20patent%20protection%20is%20needed%20to%20promote%20innovation.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20severely%20limits%20access%20to%20the%20fruits%20of%20innovation%20to%20needy%20populations%2C%20partly%20because%20knowledge%20is%20not%20shared%20and%20partly%20because%20the%20rents%20sought%20for%20intellectual%20property%20ownership%20render%20the%20output%20of%20innovation%20unaffordable%20to%20the%20majority.%20The%20failure%20to%20reach%20the%20vaccine%20to%20prevent%20or%20mitigate%20the%20effect%20of%20COVID-19%20to%20a%20majority%20across%20the%20world%2C%20with%20devastating%20consequences%2C%20is%20an%20illustration%20of%20the%20former%20tendency%2C%20and%20the%20long%20period%20during%20which%20treatment%20for%20infection%20from%20the%20AIDS%20virus%20remained%20completely%20unaffordable%20for%20affected%20populations%20is%20an%20illustration%20of%20the%20latter.%20This%20occurred%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20much%20of%20the%20science%20and%20the%20technology%20needed%20in%20both%20cases%20was%20funded%20with%20public%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20own%20experience%20illustrates%20that%20all%20is%20not%20lost%20even%20within%20the%20boundaries%20of%20a%20profit-driven%20order.%20But%20protecting%20past%20benefits%20and%20gains%20requires%20struggle%20on%20multiple%20fronts.%20There%20is%20need%20for%20struggle%20to%20democratise%20institutions%20that%20advance%20scientific%20and%20technological%20knowledge.%20Lessons%20from%20past%20successful%20efforts%20to%20limit%20and%20tweak%20intellectual%20property%20rights%2C%20as%20happened%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20now-diluted%20law%20that%20refused%20to%20grant%20or%20recognise%20product%20patents%2C%20need%20to%20be%20revisited%20and%20efforts%20to%20liberate%20the%20knowledge%20commons%20launched.%20And%20every%20effort%20must%20be%20made%20to%20conduct%20the%20now-inevitable%2C%20large-scale%20research%20in%20various%20fields%20a%20cooperative%20venture%2C%20as%20happened%20with%20the%20free%20software%20movement%20and%20with%20experiments%20in%20the%20biological%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabir%20Purkayastha%20has%2C%20as%20an%20activist%20and%20public%20intellectual%2C%20been%20and%20remains%20a%20part%20of%20that%20global%20struggle.%20But%20he%20recognises%20the%20threat%2C%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%2C%20that%20results%20from%20the%20embrace%20of%20neoliberalism%2C%20the%20associated%20redefinition%20of%20the%20role%20of%20the%20state%2C%20and%20the%20concurrent%20and%20linked%20tendency%20to%20suppress%20scientific%20and%20critical%20thinking%20in%20favour%20of%20obscurantism%20that%20celebrates%20the%20irrational.%20That%20too%20is%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20ruling%20classes%20who%20enclose%20the%20commons%20to%20further%20their%20private%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709024732000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27142248%2FUntitled-design-17.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkeeping-the-global-struggle-alive-for-freeing-up-the-commons%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prabir%20Purkayastha's%20in%20his%20latest%20book%20'Knowledge%20as%20Commons%3A%20Towards%20Inclusive%20Science%20and%20Technology'%20he%20recognises%20the%20global%20threat%20that%20results%20from%20the%20embrace%20of%20neoliberalism%2C%20the%20associated%20redefinition%20of%20the%20role%20of%20the%20state%2C%20and%20the%20tendency%20to%20suppress%20scientific%20thinking%20in%20favour%20of%20obscurantism%20that%20celebrates%20the%20irrational.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkeeping-the-global-struggle-alive-for-freeing-up-the-commons%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20war%3A%20Putin%20restructures%20Russian%20armed%20forces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709020680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108037004%2Cimgsize-19068.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3