%20a%2030-minute%20bus%20ride%20from%20Kullu%20and%20invites%20you%20to%20experience%20a%20stay%20in%20a%20traditional%20setting%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Kundan%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20dark%20settles%2C%20Kala%20gets%20to%20work%20to%20turn%20fresh%20produce%20into%20delectable%20food%2C%20and%20you%20can%20be%20a%20bystander%20to%20the%20amazing%20fare%20she%20is%20preparing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20tourists%20enjoy%20the%20culture%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Kundan%20enjoys%20hearing%20about%20theirs.%20These%20interactions%20have%20changed%20his%20mindset%20in%20many%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20belief%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F121671%2Fsaveagram-aims-at-getting-income-tourists-and-self-esteem-for-villagers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20village%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20that%20girls%20should%20be%20married%20off%20young%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20though%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20would%20send%20our%20children%20to%20school%2C%20we%20often%20had%20their%20marriage%20at%20the%20back%20of%20our%20minds.%20We%20would%20worry%20that%20once%20they%20have%20completed%20school%20we%20need%20to%20think%20about%20it.%20But%20the%20tourists%20who%20came%20to%20my%20homestay%20from%20foreign%20places%20tell%20me%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Kundan%20ji%2C%20education%20gives%20a%20better%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20began%20changing%20our%20mindset.%20Now%20I%20am%20not%20worried%20about%20my%20girls%20getting%20married%20young.%20There%20is%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20evening%20bathes%20the%20Kais%20village%20in%20a%20bluish%20tinge%2C%20it%20is%20wonderful%20to%20watch%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20family%20bustling%20about%20their%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CI%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20my%20family%20to%20see%20the%20world.%20So%2C%20I%20brought%20the%20world%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kundan%20says%2C%20rei